quran[695]{c,v,t}:
  5,1,"A wid iumnen! Eîîfet deg iâahden nnwen. Ëellen awen lmal n tejlibt, kkes ed wid i wen nnan. Ur awen têell ara ûûyada, mara têuoem. Öebbi, s tidep, Ippameô ayen i S ihwan"
  5,2,"A wid iumnen! Ur ssiôxiset isekkiren n Öebbi, aggur iôqan, îêegga, snaoeq, wid iteddun ar Uxxam n Lêaôam, saramen lfevl akked llza n Mass nnsen. Üegdet mi tfukkem. Xas tcuênem agdud i wen igedlen Loamaâ n Lêaôam, ur iwata ara a pzegrem tilas. Mâawanet ar yise$ akked uêezzeb, ur ppemâawanet ar ubekkav akked lbe$wv. Ëezzbet i Öebbi. S tidep, Öebbi Iwâaô deg uâaqeb"
  5,3,"I wen ipwagedlen d loifa, idim, aksum n yilef, wayen ipwamezlen i war Öebbi, ayen ippuxenqen, ayen i pwaûerâan, ayen igrarben, ayen ippuberrzen, ayen içça lweêc - siwa ma tessawvem tezlam t -, îêegga i tezôa, aseqdec n tseqqaôt. Ayagi d ucmit. Assa, wid ijehlen uysen si ddin nnwen. Ur ten ppagwadet, agwadet iyI. Assa, Nnekmale$ awen ddin nnwen, Tame$ awen l$it iW, Öuva$ awen annuz d ddin. Win terra tmara di tegwnip n llaé, ur iffi$ abrid, Öebbi, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu"
  5,4,"A k steqsayen acu i sen iêellen. Ini: \"iêell awen wayen imaânen. Ayen d teppawin s lewêuc ipûeggiden. Tesêefvem asen ayen i wen Isseêfev Öebbi. Eççet seg wayen i wen d îîfen, mmektit ed fellas isem n Öebbi\". Ëezzbet i Öebbi. Öebbi, s tidep, Ip$awal deg uqeîîi"
  5,5,"Assa, iêell awen wayen imaânen. Iêell awen lqut n wid iwumi teppunefk Tezmamt, - iêell asen lqut nnwen -; tilawin tiêuôiyin iumnen, tilawin tiêuôiyin seg wid iwumi teppunefk Tezmamt, uqbel nnwen, ma tefkam asent tuççit nnsent; d uwqimen maççi d ucmiten, ur teppeddum d temddukwal. Win iugin liman, mêan igiten is. Neppa, di laxeôt, seg imexsuôen"
  5,6,"A wid iumnen! Ma tekkrem ar téallit, ssirdet udmawen nnwen, ifassen nnwen alamma d ti$wmaô, sâaddit ifassen illexsen $ef iqweôôa nnwen, ssirdet ivaôen nnwen ar twelza. Ma tellam s loanaba, zzizdget. Ma tuvnem ne$ tunagem, ne$ iusa d yiwen segwen si ccicma, ne$ tennulem tilawin, ur tufim aman, ddmet akal zeddigen, sâaddit ep $ef udmawen nnwen akked ifassen nnwen. Ur Ib$a ara Öebbi a kwen Iqelleq, maca Ib$a a kwen Izzizdeg, ad awen Itim l$it iS, amar a pesnemmrem"
  5,7,"Mmektit ed l$it ikwen I$at Öebbi, akked nnesba ikwen Inuseb, mi tennam: \"nesla u nunez\". Ëezzbet i Öebbi. Öebbi, s tidep, Issen i illan deg idmaren"
  5,8,"A wid iumnen! Illit d ôôsem ar Öebbi, d inagan at lmizan. Ur kwen issencaf dd$el n ugdud, ur twezznem. Wezznet. Lmizan iqôeb aîas ar uêezzeb. Ëezzbet i Öebbi. Öebbi, s tidep, Issen ayen txeddmem"
  5,9,"Iâahed Öebbi ssmaê akked warraz ameqwôaêan, i wid iumnen, u xeddmen ayen ilhan"
  5,10,"Wid ijehlen u skaddben issekniyen nne£, widak d at ujajiê"
  5,11,"A wid iumnen! Mmektit ed l$it ikwen I$at Öebbi, amek agdud ipheggi iman is, ad isâaddi afus is fellawen. Iîîef akin ifassen nnsen, segwen. Ëezzbet i Öebbi. £ef Öebbi ara ppeklen lmumnin"
  5,12,"Ni$ Irra Öebbi laâqed i At Isôail. Nessuffe$ ed, segsen, mrawsin imvebbôen. Inna Öebbi: \"Nek yidwen ma téullem, tzekkam, tumnem s imazanen iW, u tâawnem ten, tôevlem i Öebbi aôeîîal igerzen. War ccekk, ad awen Kkse$ tucmitin nnwen, a kwen Skecme$ di leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen. Win ijehlen segwen, deffir waya, ni$ innetlaf seg ubrid umâin"
  5,13,"Imi ooan laâqed nnsen, Nexza ten, Nesgursel ulawen nnsen. Ssexsaôen inumak n wawalen, ppun amur n wayen i$ef pwafekkôen. Mazal a d temlilev d lexdaâ nnsen, siwa drus segsen. Semmeê asen u ssuref. Öebbi, s tidep, Iêemmel iâaôviyen"
  5,14,"Wid iqqaôen: \"nekwni d imasiêiyen\", Nerra laâqed yidsen, ppun amur n wayen i$ef pwafekkôen. Nessker ed, garasen, taâdawt akked dd$el, ar ass n tnekra. Deqqal a ten Ixebbeô Öebbi $ef wayen la ûenâan"
  5,15,"A yAt Tezmamt! Ni$ iusa kwen id Umazan nne£. Ad awen ibeggen aîas n wayen la teppeffrem, n Tezmamt. Ad Ipsemmiê i waîas. Ni$ tusa kwen id tafat s$uô Öebbi, akked Tezmamt ipbegginen"
  5,16,"Inehhu yis Öebbi, ar iberdan n tifrat, wid iôe$ben llza S. A ten Issuffe$ si tillas ar tafat, s tsriê iS. A ten Inhu s abrid uwqim"
  5,17,"Ni$ jehlen wid innan: \"Öebbi, s tidep, d lmasiê, mmi s n Meryem\". Ini: \"anwa isâan kra n lkwelf, s$uô Öebbi, ma ihwa yaS ad Ine$ lmasiê, mmi s n Meryem, imma s, akked wayen akw illan di tmurt\"? N Öebbi tagelda n tmurt, igenwan, akked wayen illan garasen. Ixelleq ayen i S ihwan. Öebbi Izmer i yal cci"
  5,18,"Udayen akked imasiêiyen, nnan: \"nekwni d tarwa n Öebbi, d wid Ismenyaf\". Ini: \"acimi, ihi, ikwen Ipâaqab $ef ibekkaven nnwen? Xaîi, kunwi d imexlaq am wiyav\". Ad Isemmeê i win i S ihwan, ad Iâaqeb win i S ihwan. N Öebbi tagelda n tmurt, igenwan, akked wayen illan garasen. Taggara $uôeS"
  5,19,"A yAt Tezmamt! Ni$ iusa kwen id Umazan nne£, ad awen ibeggen, mi tâadda tallit war imazanen. Akka ur d teqqaôem ara: \"ur a$ d iusi ubeccaô, ne$ uneddaô\". Ihi, iusa kwen id ubeccaô, uneddaô. Öebbi Izmer i yal cci"
  5,20,"Mi inna Musa i ugdud is: \"a yagdud iw! Mmektit ed l$it ikwen I$at Öebbi. Irra segwen lambiyya, Irra kwen d igeldan. Ifka yawen ayen ur Ifki i yiwen, deg imavalen"
  5,21,"A yagdud iw! Kecmet akal iôqan, i wen Iura Öebbi. Ur d ppu$alet $er deffir wen, a d tegwrim txesôem"
  5,22,"Nnan: \"a Musa! Degs agdud iâafriten, nekwni ur p nkeççem, d awez$i, alamma ff$en d segs. Mi d ff$en segs, a nekcem"
  5,23,"Sin irgazen, seg wid iugaden - Isâad iten Öebbi -, nnan: \"kecmet $uôsen si tebburt; ma tkecmem, kunwi, ih, a prebêem. Ppeklet af Öebbi, ma d lmumnin ay tellam"
  5,24,"Nnan: \"a Musa! Nekwni ur p nkeççem, d awez$i, skud mazal iten degs. Öuê, keçç d Mass ik, nna$et. Nekwni a neqqim dagi"
  5,25,"Inna: \"a Mass iw! Ay melke$, nek, siwa iman iw akked gma; ihi, Semfaôeq a$ d ugdud"
  5,26,"Inna: \"ihi, tamurt agi tepwagdel asen. Ukuéet iseggwasen ad menîaôen di lberr. Ur $webben $ef ugdud iballa$en"
  5,27,"Eêku yasen, s tidep, taqûit n sin warrac n Adem, mi îêeggan i sin. S$uô yiwen tepwaqbel. S$uô wayev ur tepwaqbel ara. Inna: \"war ccekk, a k n$e$\". Inna: \"Iqebbel kan Öebbi îêegga s$uô wid ipêezziben"
  5,28,"Ma ibbwev iyi d ufus ik, ad iyi ten$ev, nek, ur k id ippawev ufus iw, a k n$e$. Nek, ppagwade$ Öebbi, Mass imavalen"
  5,29,"Nek, b$i$ a ppawiv abekkav iw, akked ubekkav ik, a ppiliv seg wat tmes. Winna d aqeîîi imednas"
  5,30,"Iaâzem, deg iman is, ad ine$ gma s, d$a in$a t. Igwra d seg imexsuôen"
  5,31,"Iuzen ed Öebbi tagerfa, tkeôôev akal, iwakken ad as tessenâat amek ara i$umm loeppa n gma s. Inna: \"a ssexv iw! Ur bbwive$ ad ili$ am tgerfa yagi, ad $umme$ loeppa n gma\". Igwra d seg wid inedmen"
  5,32,"Ilmend n waya, Nura i At Isôail, ar win in$an amdan ur nen$i yiwen, ur nessefsed di tmurt, amzun in$a imdanen meôôa. Win issadren yiwen, amzun issader imdanen meôôa. Ni$ usan ten id imazanen nne£, s ubeggen. Sinna, deffir waya, s tidep, aîas degsen ssuguten di tmurt"
  5,33,"Aqeîîi n wid ipna$en Öebbi akked Umazan iS, u ssenkaren asefsed di tmurt, siwa timen$iwt, ne$ asemmeô $ef umidag, ne$ anegzum ufus sya, uvaô sya, ne$ anfay si tmurt. Ayagi, d aqeîîi nnsen di ddunit. Di laxeôt, fellasen aâaqeb ameqwôaêan"
  5,34,"Kkes ed wid inedmen, uqbel a pvebbôem fellasen. Cfut ar Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu"
  5,35,"A wid iumnen! Ëezzbet i Öebbi, nadit a pqeôôbem $uôeS, nna$et deg ubrid iS, amar a prebêem"
  5,36,"Ih, wid ijehlen, xas ad sâun i illan akw di tmurt, rnu yas win i t icban, iwakken ad fdun, yis, iman nnsen seg uâaqeb, ass n tnekra, ur ipwaqbal segsen. Fellasen aâaqeb aqeôêan"
  5,37,"Ad b$un a d ff$en si tmes, ur llin d wid id iteff$en. Fellasen aâaqeb imezgi"
  5,38,"Amakwar, tamakwart, gezmet asen ifassen nnsen, d aqeîîi n wayen xedmen, d aâaqeb s$uô Öebbi. Öebbi d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab"
  5,39,"Win inedmen, deffir ddens is, u iu$al d aâôvi, ad as Issuref Öebbi. Öebbi, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu"
  5,40,"Day ur teéôiv ara n Öebbi tagelda n tmurt akked igenwan? Ipâaqab win i S ihwan, Ipsemmiê i win i S ihwan. Öebbi Izmer i yal cci"
  5,41,"A Nnbi! Ur k $weblen wid ip$awalen ar tijehli, seg wid iqqaôen numen, s imawen nnsen, ur uminen wulawen nnsen, seg wudayen issemêasen i tikerkas, issemêasen i ugdud nniven, ur d nusi $uôek. Pbeddilen awalen deffir ussefhem nnsen. Qqaôen: \"ma ippunefk awen d waya, ddemt ep; ma ur awen d ippunefk ara, $uôwat\"! Win Ib$a Öebbi a t Ihewwel, ur t tepsellikev, s wacemma, seg ufus n Öebbi. Widak, d wid iwumi ur Ib$a ara Öebbi, ad izdigen wulawen nnsen. Di ddunit ad pwaxzun. Di laxeôt fellasen aâaqeb abarar"
  5,42,"Wid issemêasen i tikerkas, iteppen leêôam, ma usan k id, fru garasen, ne$ eoo iten. Ma teooiv ten, ur k îîuôôun s wacemma. Ma têuddev, êudd garasen s lmizan. Öebbi, s tidep, Iêemmel wid iweznen"
  5,43,"Amek ara k id asen, s aêuddu, u nitni sâan Tuôa, degs aêuddu n Öebbi? Sinna, deffir waya, ad wexxôen. Ur llin wigi si lmumnin"
  5,44,"Ih, Nessers ed Tuôa, degs nnhaya akked tafat, ferrun yis ger wudayen, lambiyya imvuâen. U iôabaniyen akked lecyux seg wayen jemâen, si Tezmamt n Öebbi, u llan d inagan is. Ur ppagwadet imdanen, agwadet iyI. Ur d ppa$et, s issekniyen iW, ayen ôxisen. Wid ur nepêuddu yara s wayen id Issers Öebbi, widak d ijehliyen"
  5,45,"Nura yasen degs: ôôuê s ôôuê, tiî s tiî, anzaren s wanzaren, ameééu$ s umeééu$, tu$mest s tu$mest, leoruê ad ppuêesben. Win iooan, d le$ôama s. Wid ur nepêuddu yara s wayen id Issers Öebbi, widak d imednas"
  5,46,"Nuzen ed, deffir sen, Âisa, mmi s n Meryem, a d itebbet ayen it id izwaren di Tuôa. Nefka yas Linoil, degs nnhaya akked tafat, a d itebbet ayen it id izwaren di Tuôa. D nnhaya u d anabi i wid ipêezziben"
  5,47,"At Linoil, iwata ad êudden s wayen id Issers, degs, Öebbi. Wid ur nêudd ara s wayen id Issers Öebbi, widak d iballa$en"
  5,48,"Nessers ak d Tazmamt, s tidep, a d tebbet ayen ip id izwaren n Tezmamt. Nvemn ip. Ihi, êudd garasen s wayen id Issers Öebbi. Ur teddu d lhawiyyat nnsen, beôôa n wayen i k id iusan n tidep. I yal wa, Nefka lqanun akked ubrid. Lemmer i S ihwi i Öebbi, yili Irra kwen d yiwen n lois. Maca, iwakken a kwen Ijeôôeb $ef wayen i wen Ifka, mzizlet ar lxiô. Ar Öebbi tu$alin nnwen akw. A kwen Ixebbeô $ef wayen tellam temgarradem"
  5,49,"Ëudd garasen s wayen id Issers Öebbi. Ur teddu d lhawiyyat nnsen. £uôek a k hewwlen $ef kra seg wayen i k d Issers Öebbi. Ma wexxôen, éeô ar Öebbi Ib$a kan a ten Iwwet $ef kra ibekkaven nnsen. Ih, aîas n medden d iballa$en"
  5,50,"Day b$an aêuddu n zzman n war tussna? Anwa yifen Öebbi d Amêaddi, i ugdud ineûêen liman"
  5,51,"A wid iumnen! Ur pparat, d iêbiben, udayen akked imasiêiyen. Garasen d iêbiben. Win, segwen, i ten irran d iêbiben, ad yili segsen. Öebbi, s tidep, ur Inehhu agdud imednas"
  5,52,"A pwaliv imuvan n wul, ppazzalen $uôsen, qqaôen asen: \"nugad ay d itezzin fella$\". Ahat a d Ias Öebbi s l$elb, ne$ s lameô s$uôeS. A d gwrin di nndama, $ef wayen ffren deg iman nnsen"
  5,53,"A d inin wid iumnen: \"day d wigi i iggullen s Öebbi, tagallit meqqwôen, ar nitni llan yidwen\"? Mêan igiten nnsen, gwran d d imexsuôen"
  5,54,"A wid iumnen! Win segwen iooan ddin is…, ihi, deqqal Öebbi a d Iawi agdud Iêemmel, i T iêemmlen; ad ôavin lmumnin, ad qesêen ar ijehliyen. Ad nna$en deg ubrid n Öebbi. Ur ppagwaden alummu n win iplummun. Ayagi d lfevl n Öebbi, Ippak it i win i S ihwan. Öebbi d Ajemmal, d Amusnaw"
  5,55,"Imawlan nnwen siwa Öebbi akked Umazan iS, wid iumnen, wid ipéallan, pzekkin, u nitni îîinizen"
  5,56,"Wid irran d imawlan nnsen, Öebbi, Amazan iS, akked wid iumnen…, ih, akabar n Öebbi, d nitni ara irebêen"
  5,57,"A wid iumnen! Ur pparat d iêbiben wid id ilhan, di ddin nnwen, s wurar d utihi, seg wid iwumi teppunefk Tezmamt, uqbel nnwen, akw seg ijehliyen. Ëezzbet i Öebbi, ma d lmumnin ay tellam"
  5,58,"Ma teddnem i téallit, fellas ad mmaâlken, ad uraren. Ayagi, acku nitni d agdud ur nefhim"
  5,59,"Ini: \"a yAt Tezmamt! Acu i$ef la $ ttehmem, siwa imi numen s Öebbi, akked wayen id Issers $uône$, akked wayen id Issers uqbel? Tegwti degwen d iballa$en"
  5,60,"Ini: \"ad awen mle$ aqeîîi n Öebbi icemten sennig wagi? Wid Ixza Öebbi, sserfan T, Irra ten d iddawen, d ilfawen\". Âabden iôebbiten n tkerkas. Widak, atnan di liêala tucmip mavi, di ttelfan u$miq seg ubrid uûwib"
  5,61,"Mi d usan $uôwen, qqaôen: \"numen\". Ni$ kecmen d s tijehli, u nitni ff$en yis. Öebbi Yif akw akken Issen, ayen teffren"
  5,62,"La tepwaliv aîas, degsen, p$awalen ar ubekkav akked wanfal, teppen leêôam. I icmet wayen xeddmen"
  5,63,"A lemmer i sen kksen iôabiyen akked lecyax, awal ubekkav akked wuççi n leêôam? I icmet wayen la ûenâen"
  5,64,"Qqaôen wudayen: \"iskkweô ufus n Öebbi\". D ifassen nnsen i isekkwôen. Pwaxzan ilmend n wayen d qqaôen. Xaîi! Ifassen iS llin, Ip$iti akken i S ihwa. Ayen i k d irsen, s$uô Mass ik, war ccekk, irennu i waîas segsen, leb$wev akked tijehli. Nessker garasen cceêna, akked dd$el, ar ass n tnekra. Yal tikelt ara caâlen times i îôad, a p Issexsi Öebbi. Pnadin asefsed di tmurt. Öebbi ur Iêemmel ara ifessaden"
  5,65,"At Tezmamt, lemmer day umnen u êezzben, yili, war ccekk, Nekkes asen tucmitin nnsen, u Nesskecm iten ar leonanat isaâdiyen"
  5,66,"Lemmer day îîifen di Tuôa akked Linoil, akked wayen i sen d irsen s$uô Mass nnsen, war ccekk, ad ççen sennig sen, akw seddaw ivaôen nnsen. Illa garasen lois iôeznen. Aîas, degsen, dirit wayen xeddmen"
  5,67,"A yAmazan, mel ayen i k d irsen, s$uô Mass ik. Ma ur t temliv ara, ur tessawvev ara tabrap iS. Öebbi a k Ifukk si l$aci. Öebbi, s tidep, ur Inehhu agdud ijehliyen"
  5,68,"Ini: \"a yAt Tezmamt! Ur tellim deg wacemma, alamma teddam d Tuôa, Linoil, akked wayen i wen d irsen, s$uô Mass nnwen\". Ayen i k d irsen s$uô Mass ik, war ccekk, irennu, i waîas segsen, leb$wev akked tijehli. Ur $webbel $ef ugdud ijehliyen"
  5,69,"Ih, wid iumnen, udayen, iûabiyen, imasiêiyen, wid iumnen s Öebbi akked wass aneggaru, u xeddmen ayen ilhan, ur ppagwaden, ur $weblen"
  5,70,"Ni$ Nga laâqed i At Isôail, Nuzen asen imazanen. Yal tikelt ara ten id ias umazan s wayen ur asen nehwi, wa a t skiddben, wa a t n$en"
  5,71,"£ilen ur ippili uhewwel. Dre$len, âaégen. Sinna, Issuref asen Öebbi. Sinna, aîas degsen dre$len, âaégen. Öebbi Ipwali acu xeddmen"
  5,72,"Ni$ jehlen wid iqqaôen: \"Öebbi, s tidep, d lmasiê, mmi s n Meryem\". U inna lmasiê: \"a yAt Isôail! Âabdet Öebbi, Mass iw, d Mass nnwen\". Ih, win icerken i Öebbi, Igdel as Öebbi Loennet. Axxam is d times. Ur llin isellaken i imednas"
  5,73,"Ni$ jehlen wid iqqaôen: \"Ih, Öebbi d wis krav n krav\". Ur illi ôebbi siwa Öebbi Yiwen. Ma ur xvin ara i wayen qqaôen, war ccekk, aâaqeb aqeôêan ad iêaz wid ijehlen segsen"
  5,74,"Day ur tuben ara ar Öebbi, u ssuturen aS ssmaê? Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu"
  5,75,"Lmasiê, mmi s n Meryem, d amazan kan. Ni$ âaddan, uqbel is, imazanen. Imma s tessawal tidep. Llan teppen lqut. Wali amek i asen Nepbeggin issekniyen; sinna, wali amek la ppagwin"
  5,76,"Ini: \"day a ppaâbdem, war Öebbi, ayen ur nezmir a kwen ivuôô, ne$ a kwen infaâ\"? Öebbi, Neppa, Issel, d Amusnaw"
  5,77,"Ini: \"a yAt Tezmamt! Ur rennut, di ddin nnwen, ayen ur nelli d tidep. Ur teddut d lemcihwat n ugdud innetlafen zik, i itelfen aîas, u telfen seg ubrid uûwib"
  5,78,"Pwaxzan wid ijehlen, seg wAt Isôail, s$uô iles n Dawed akked Âisa, mmi s n Meryem; ayagi, $ef wayen âuûan, u zgaren tilas"
  5,79,Ur ppemyekkasen ayen xedmen n dir. I icmet wayen xeddmen
  5,80,"A pwaliv aîas segsen, ad xalven wid ijehlen. War ccekk, icmet wayen xedmen i iman nnsen. Ad Izâaf Öebbi fellasen. Nitni ad wekkôen deg uâaqeb"
  5,81,"Lemmer uminen s Öebbi, Nnbi, akked wayen i sen d irsen, ur ten pparan d iêbiben. Maca aîas, segsen, d iballa$en"
  5,82,"A ppafev icenga iqeûêanen mavi, n wid iumnen, d udayen akked wid ipcaraken. A ppafev wid iqeôben mavi, s lmaênana, ar wid iumnen, d wid innan: \"nekwni d imasiêiyen\". Ayagi, acku llan degsen ixelwiyen, iôehbaniyen, u nitni ur sme$wôen ara iman nnsen"
  5,83,"Ma slan i wayen id iusan ar Umazan, a pwaliv allen nnsen ççuôent d imeîîi, seg wayen ufan n tidep. Qqaôen: \"a Mass nne$! Numen, Aru ya$ seg inagan"
  5,84,"Acu i $ iu$en ur numin s Öebbi akked wayen i $ d iusan n tidep; ur nessarem a $ Issekcem, Mass nne$, s agdud iâaôviyen"
  5,85,"A ten Ioazi Öebbi, $ef wayen d qqaôen, s leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, degsen ad wekkôen. Wagi d aoazi n lâuûam"
  5,86,"Wid ijehlen, u skaddben issekniyen nne£, widak, d at Loahennama"
  5,87,"A wid iumnen! Ur pgeddilet ayen imaânen i wen Iêell Öebbi. Ur zegret tilas. Öebbi, s tidep, ur Iêemmel ara wid izegren tilas"
  5,88,"Eççet seg wayen ikwen Iôéeq Öebbi, iêellen, imaânen. Ëezzbet i Öebbi. YiS, kunwi, ay tumnem"
  5,89,"Ur kwen Ipqassa Öebbi $ef tgallit n tkerkas. Maca, a kwen Iqiss $ef tgallit n ûûeê. Takweffaôt is: a ppecceççem mraw ime$ban, akken tecceççam tawacult nnwen, ne$ a ten tesselsem, ne$ a pserêem i wakli. Win ur nwâa ara, ad iuéum krav wussan. D tagi ay d takweffaôt n tgallit nnwen, ma teggullem. Eîîfet di tgallit nnwen. Akka i wen d Ipbeggin Öebbi issekniyen, amar a ppesnemmrem"
  5,90,"A wid iumnen! Ccôab, leqwmeô, tiâancuôin, taseqqaôt, d ayen kan icemten, seg igi n Cciîan. Ihi, veôôeft asen, amar a prebêem"
  5,91,"Ib$a kan Cciîan ad isker ticenga akked dd$el garawen, s ccôab akked leqwmeô, a kwen iveôôef seg usmekti n Öebbi, akked téallit. Day ur tepfukkum ara"
  5,92,"A$et awal i Öebbi, a$et awal i Umazan. £uôwat! Ma twexxôem, cfut ar Amazan, iwata yas kan anabi ipbegginen"
  5,93,"Ur telli tiyta deg wid iumnen, u xeddmen ayen ilhan, $ef wayen ççan, ma êezzben, umnen, xedmen ayen ilhan, sinna êezzben, umnen, sinna, êezzben u maânen. Öebbi Iêemmel lâuûam"
  5,94,"A wid iumnen! War ccekk, a kwen Iweddeb Öebbi $ef wayen tepûeggidem s ifassen nnwen, u s ixtucen nnwen, iwakken ad Iéeô Öebbi anwa i T ippagwaden, di tbavnit. Win izegren tilas, deffir waya, fellas aâaqeb aqeôêan"
  5,95,"A wid iumnen! Ur pûeggidet di zzyaôa nnwen. Win iûeggden segwen, u iâammed, aqeîîi: ad iseddeq, si lmal is, ayen in$a s ûûyada s, a d êudden, f waya, sin irgazen iêesbiyen segwen. D tikci ara iawven ar Lkaâba. Ne$ takweffaôt: ad icceçç ime$ban, ne$, ayen iswan aya, ad iuéum. Ad ijeôôeb vveôô n lameô is. Öebbi Isemmeê i wayen iâaddan. Win iu$alen a d Irr Öebbi segs ppaô. Öebbi d Uzmir, Ippara d ppaô"
  5,96,"Têell awen ûûyada n yill akked uççi s. D lqut i kunwi akw iminigen. Tepwagdel awen ûûyada di tmurt, skud aql akwen d zziyyaô. Ëezzbet i Öebbi, $uôeS ara tepwafesrem"
  5,97,"Irra Öebbi Lkaâba d axxam iôqan ipwabnan i l$aci, aggur iôqan, asfel, isenoaq, ayagi iwakken a ppeéôem ar Öebbi Iéôa i illan deg igenwan u di tmurt, u Öebbi Issen yal cci"
  5,98,"Cfut iwâaô uâaqeb n Öebbi. Öebbi, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu"
  5,99,"Amazan, iwata yas kan unabi. Öebbi Iéôa ayen temmalem u ayen teppeffrem"
  5,100,"Ini: \"ur iaâdil ara wayen n dir akked wayen imaânen\", xas teswehm ik lkwetôa n wayen n dir. Ëezzbet i Öebbi, a yuâqilen, amar a prebêem"
  5,101,"A wid iumnen! Ur steqsayet $ef t$awsiwin ara kwen icwe$ben, ma mlan awen tent. Ma testeqsam fellasent mara d iprusu Leqwôan, ad awen ppufessrent. Öebbi Isemmeê aya. Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Iêellem"
  5,102,"Ni$ isteqsa fellasent ugdud, uqbel nnwen. Sinna, segsent, gwran d d ijehliyen"
  5,103,"Ur d Ifki Öebbi Baêiôa, ne$ Sayba, ne$ Waûila, ne$ Ëami. Maca, wid ijehlen gren d tikerkas $ef Öebbi. Tegwti degsen ur fhimen"
  5,104,"Ma nnan asen: \"yyaw ar wayen id Issers Öebbi, u ar Umazan\". Qqaôen: \"beôka ya$ ayen id nufa, $ef waya, $eô imezwura nne$\". I ma imezwura nnsen ur ssinen acemma, ur pwanhan"
  5,105,"A wid iumnen! Fellawen iman nnwen. Ur kwen iîîuôôu win innetlafen, ma tepwanham. Ar Öebbi, tu$alin nnwen akw. A kwen Ixebbeô $ef wayen txeddmem"
  5,106,"A wid iumnen! Ccada garawen, ma tusa d tmeppant ar yiwen segwen. Di lawan uweûûi, sin irgazen iêesbiyen, segwen, ne$ wiyav war segwen, ma tellam d iminigen di tmurt, u tusa kwen id twa$it n tmeppant. A ten qesden deffir téallit. Ma tcukkem, sgallet pen s Öebbi: \"ur d nesfayday syis, xas iaâna llzem nne$, ur nteffer ccada n Öebbi, mulac, nekwni a nili seg imednab"
  5,107,"Ma ivehô ed fellasen denben, ad ppuneûfen s wiyav, si loiha n wid vuôôen imezwura. Ad ggalen s Öebbi: \"ih, ccada nne$ tif ccada nnsen. Ur nzegger tilas, mulac, war ccekk, a nili seg imednas"
  5,108,"Ppif akka iwakken a d awin ccada iwulmen, ad agwaden a ppili tgallit deffir tgallit nnsen. Ëezzbet i Öebbi, ssemêesset, Öebbi ur Inehhu agdud iballa$en"
  5,109,"Ass ideg ara Issemlil Öebbi imazanen, ad Yini: \"acu i wen d jawben\"? Ad inin: \"ur telli tussna $uône$. D Keçç, s tidep, i Issnen tibavniyin"
  5,110,"Mi Inna Öebbi: \"a Âisa, mmi s n Meryem! Mmekti d i kwen £$ate$, keçç akked imma k, mi k Âiwne$ s ôôuê iôqan. Tepmmeslayev i medden si dduê, am unqaqôi. Mi k Slemde$ Tazmamt, ûûwab, Tuôa, Linoil. Mi tûenâav, si talaxt, ûûifa n ufrux, s– tsriê iW; tûuvev degs, tu$al d afôux, s– tsriê iW. Tesseêlayev agugam, amuvin n lberû, s– tsriê iW. Mi tessenkarev lmeggtin, s– tsriê iW. Mi Sbaâde$ fellak At Isôail, mi d tusiv $uôsen, s ubeggen, u nnan wid ijehlen segsen: \"ayagi iban d ssêur kan"
  5,111,"Mi Weêêa$ i inmahalen: \"amnet yissI, akw s umazan iW\". Nnan: \"numen. Echhed ar nekwni d imvuâen"
  5,112,"Mi nnan inmahalen: \"a Âisa, mmi s n Meryem! Ma Izmer Mass ik ad a$ d Issers lmaida seg igenni\"? Inna: \"êezzbet i Öebbi, ma d lmumnin ay tellam"
  5,113,"Nnan: \"neb$a a neçç segs, a nevmen ulawen nne$, a néeô ar tenniv a$ d tidep, a nili d inagan iS"
  5,114,"Inna Âisa, mmi s n Meryem: \"a Öebbi, Mass nne$, Ssers a$ d lmaida, seg igenni, ad a$ tili d lâid i umezwaru u i uneggaru nne$, u d assekni s $uôeK. £it a$ d. Keçç, Tifev akw im$iten"
  5,115,"Inna Öebbi: \"ad awen p id Sserse$. Win ijehlen segwen, deffir waya, a t Âaqbe$ aâaqeb ur Sâadda$ i yiwen deg imavalen"
  5,116,"Mi Inna Öebbi: \"a Âisa, mmi s n Meryem! D keçç i innan i l$aci: erret a$, nek akked imma, d sin iôebbiten war Öebbi\"? Inna: \"gedha s yiseK! Ur iyi ippunefk ara a d ini$ ayen i$ef ur sâi$ lêeqq. Lemmer i t id nni$, yili Teéôiv t. Tesnev i illan deg iman iw, ur ssine$ ayen illan deg iman iK. Keçç, s tidep, d Amusnaw n tbavniyin"
  5,117,"I asen nni$, siwa ayen iyi d Tumôev: âabdet Öebbi, Mass iw, u Mass nnwen. Lli$ d anagi nnsen, skud lli$ garasen. Mi iyi n Tessuliv $uôeK, d Keçç i ten id Iquôâan. Keçç, d Anagi n yal cci"
  5,118,"Ma Tâaqbev ten, ni$ d imdanen iK, ma Tsemmêev asen, Keçç, s tidep, d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab"
  5,119,"Inna Öebbi: \"wagi d ass ideg ara stenfâan imawlan n tidep, si tidep nnsen. I nitni leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, ad wekkôen degsen, i lebda\". Iôuva ten Öebbi, u ôuvan T, d wagi ay d rrbeê ameqwôaêan"
  5,120,"N Öebbi tagelda n tmurt akked igenwan, akked wayen illan degsen. Neppa Izmer i yal cci"
  6,1,"A neckeô Öebbi i Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan. Irra tillas, tafat. Sinna, wid ijehlen pparan tanudda i Mass nnsen"
  6,2,"Neppa, ikwen Ixelqen s talaxt, sinna, Iseyya lajel. £uôeS lajel ipwassnen. Deffir waya, kunwi la tepcukkum"
  6,3,"Neppa, d Öebbi deg igenwan, di tmurt. Issen sser nnwen, d wayen d teqqaôem. Iéôa ayen tkesbem"
  6,4,"Ur ten id ippas ussekni seg issekniyen n Mass nnsen, mebla ma ugin t"
  6,5,"Ni$ skaddben tidep, mi ten id tusa. A ten id ias usali n wayen i$ef ttihin"
  6,6,"Day ur walan ara acêal isuta, uqbel nnsen, ay Nekkes. Nesserked iten di tmurt akken ur kwen Nesserked. Nuzen asen aîas ugeffur, Nerra yasen isaffen, ppazzalen seddawat sen. Nesnegr iten ilmend ibekkaven nnsen. Nxelq ed, deffir sen, sself nniven"
  6,7,"Xas ad ak ed Nessers Tazmamt, di lka$ev, ara nnalen s ifassen nnsen, war ccekk, a d inin wid ijehlen: \"wagi, s tidep, siwa ssêur n ûûeê"
  6,8,"Qqaôen: \"a lemmer id irs $uôes lmelk\". Lemmer a n Nessers lmelk, war ccekk, ad iûaô lameô, sinna, ur pganin"
  6,9,"Lemmer i t Nerri d lmelk, yili Nerra t d argaz, ad as Nessels ayen plusun"
  6,10,"Ni$ mmaâlken $ef imazanen, uqbel ik. Ayen i$ef ttihin, izzi i wid, segsen, immaâlken"
  6,11,"Ini: \"ddut di tmurt, sinna walit amek tevôa d wid iskiddiben"
  6,12,"Ini: \"w i t ilan wayen akw illan di tmurt akked igenwan\"? Ini: \"d Öebbi\". Iura, deg iman iS, aêunu. A kwen Issemlil i wass n tnekra, ur ccekk fellas. Wid isxesôen iman nnsen, ur ppamnen"
  6,13,"IneS i ized$en deg iv, deg wass. Neppa Issel, d Amusnaw"
  6,14,"Ini: \"day ara sâu$ bab, war Öebbi, Axellaq n tmurt akked igenwan? Neppa Icceççay ur t cceççayen\". Ini: \"nek pwamôe$ d ad ili$ d amenzu ara ianzen. Ur ppilit seg imcurak"
  6,15,"Ini: \"nek ugade$, ma aâûa$ Mass iw, aâaqeb n wass ameqwôaêan"
  6,16,"Win imenâan segs, assen, ni$ Iêun fellas. Wagi d rrebê n ûûeê"
  6,17,"Ma Isâadda Öebbi fellak cedda, ur p itekkes yiwen, siwa Neppa. Ma Isrebê ik, Neppa Izmer i yal cci"
  6,18,"D Neppa ay d Aqehhaô, sennig imdanen iS; d Neppa ay d Bab n ûûwab, i Iéôan"
  6,19,"Ini: \"anda p ccada sennig akw tiyav\"? Ini: \"Öebbi d Anagi gari yidwen. Iweêêa yi d Leqwôan agi, iwakken a kwen nabi$ yis, kunwi akked wid u$uô ibbwev. Day, kunwi, war ccekk, a pcehhdem ar, ar tama n Öebbi, llan iôebbiten nniven\"? Ini: \"ur cehhde$\"! Ini: \"Neppa d Öebbi, siwa Yiwen. Nek, rri$ akin ayen tepcarakem"
  6,20,"Wid iwumi Nefka Tazmamt, ssnen p, akken ssnen arraw nnsen. Wid isxesôen iman nnsen, ihi, ur ppamnen"
  6,21,"Anwa idensen sennig win d igren tikerkas $ef Öebbi, ne$ iskaddben issekniyen iS? Ih, ur rebêen imednas"
  6,22,"Ass ideg ara ten Nefser meôôa, sinna a Nini i wid icurken: \"anda ten icriken nnwen, i la tâabdem"
  6,23,"Deg uhewwel nnsen, siwa ma nnan d: \"s Öebbi, Mass nne$, ur nelli d imcurak"
  6,24,Wali amek skaddben $ef yiman nnsen. Itelf iten wayen la d snulfuyen
  6,25,"Garasen wid i k issemêasen. Nerra aêurrim $ef ulawen nnsen, iwakken ur t fehmen. Tiâééegt deg imeééu$en nnsen. Ma walan yal assekni, ur ppamnen yis. Alamma, ma usan d $uôek, a k namren, ad ak inin wid ijehlen: ayagi siwa tiêkayin imezwura"
  6,26,"Sîixxiôen segs, îîeôôifen segs. Ay squccun siwa iman nnsen, ur faqen"
  6,27,"Lemmer a ten twaliv, mara bedden ar tmes, a d inin: a ssexv nne$! Awi $ irran, ur neskiddib issekniyen n Mass nne$! A nili si lmumnin"
  6,28,"Xaîi! Iban asen d wayen teffren, zik. Lemmer a d kren, ad u$alen ar wayen i sen ipwagedlen. Nitni, s tidep, d ikeddaben"
  6,29,"U qqaôen: \"siwa tameddurt n ddunit i illan. Nekwni, ur fella$ tanekra"
  6,30,"Lemmer a pwaliv mara bedden ar Mass nnsen, ad Yini: \"ni$ ayagi s tidep\"? A d inin: \"ih, s Mass nne$\"! Ad Yini: \"ihi jeôôbet aâaqeb, ilmend n wayen tejhilem"
  6,31,"Ni$ xesôen wid iskaddben timlilit akked öÖebbi. Alamma, ma iusa ten id yimir, deqzalla, a d inin: \"a yamxix nne$, $ef wayen ideg nestehza\"! Nitni ad bibben tiâakkwumin nnsen $ef izugar nnsen. I icmet wayen bubben"
  6,32,"Tameddurt n ddunit d urar kan akked lhawiyya. Axxam aneggaru, war ccekk, yif ip i wid ipêezziben. Day ur tepmeyyizem ara"
  6,33,"Ni$ Neéôa i$webben ik, s tidep, wayen qqaôen. Ihi, nitni ur k skiddiben. Maca imednas veggôen issekniyen n Öebbi"
  6,34,"Ni$ skaddben imazanen uqbel ik. Üebôen $ef wayen i ten skaddben, akked wayen i ten meêênen, armi i ten id iusa usellek nne£. Ur illi ubeddel i wawalen n Öebbi. Ni$ usan k id, kra isallen imazanen"
  6,35,"Ma ééay fellak uwexxeô nnsen, ma tzemôev a tessarmev aderbuz di tmurt, ne$ sellum s igenni, ad asen d tawiv assekni. Ma ihwa yaS i Öebbi, a ten Issemlil ar nnhaya. Ur ppili seg wid ur nessin"
  6,36,"Siwa wid isellen, ara d ijawben. Lmegtin a ten id Issker Öebbi, sinna, $uôeS tu$alin nnsen"
  6,37,"Qqaôen: \"acimi ur as d irs ara ussekni s$uô Mass is\"? Ini: \"Öebbi, s tidep, Izmer a d Issers assekni\", maca tegwti degsen ur éôin"
  6,38,"Ur illi lweêc di tmurt, ne$ ufrux ippafgen s wafriwen is, ur nelli d leoyus am kunwi. Ur Nestehza, di Tezmamt, $ef wacemma. Sinna, ar Mass nnsen, ad pwafessren"
  6,39,"Wid iskaddben issekniyen nne£, âaégen, gugmen, di tillas. Win i S ihwan i Öebbi, a t Itlef. Win i S ihwan, a t Iawi d ubrid uwqim"
  6,40,"Ini: \"twalam ma iusa kwen id uâaqeb n Öebbi, ne$ ma iusa kwen id yimir, day ar war Öebbi ara tnaâôem, ma tessawalem tidep"
  6,41,"Xaîi! £uôeS ara tnujem. Ad Issiferr ayen i$ef tnujem $uôeS, ma ihwa yaS, a ppeppum ayen tcurkem"
  6,42,"Ni$ Nuzen ed ar leoyus, uqbel ik. Nesâadda fellasen tilufa, ccqa, amar ad êiwten"
  6,43,"A lemmer êawten, mi ten id tusa tiyta nne£. Maca, qehôen wulawen nnsen. Cciîan Icebbeê asen ayen xeddmen"
  6,44,"Mi ppun ayen i sen d smmektin, Nelli yasen tibbura n yal cci, armi, mi feôêen s wayen i sen ippunefken, Newwet iten, deqzalla. D$a qevâen layas"
  6,45,"Pwakksen wid id igwran seg ugdud idensen. Ccekôan i Öebbi, Mass imavalen"
  6,46,"Ini: \"twalam, ma Iddem awen Öebbi timesliwt nnwen, akked iéôi nnwen; ma Isle$ ulawen nnwen; anwa ôebbi, war Öebbi, ar awen ten id iawin\"? Wali amek Nessefham issekniyen, u nitni, sinna, zzin akin"
  6,47,"Ini: \"acu twalam, ma iusa kwen id uâaqeb n Öebbi, deqzalla, ne$ âinani? Day ara Ine$, siwa agdud imednas"
  6,48,"Ur d Nuzen imazanen, siwa i ubecceô, d unabi. Wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, ur ppagwaden, ur $weblen"
  6,49,"Wid iskaddben issekniyen nne£, a ten iêaz uâaqeb, ilmend n wayen be$wven"
  6,50,"Ini: \"ur awen qqare$ sâi$ igerrujen n Öebbi, ur ssine$ tabavnit; ur awen qqare$: nek, d lmelk. Nek, teddu$ kan akked wayen iyi d ippuweêêan\". Ini: \"day iaâdel uder$al d win ipwalin? Day ur d tepmeyyizem ara"
  6,51,"Nabi yis wid iugaden ad pwafessren ar Mass nnsen. Ur sâin bab, war Neppa, ne$ amcafaâ. Amar ad êezzben"
  6,52,"Ur ppara wid ipnujun $uô Mass nnsen, taûebêit, tameddit, pnadin udem iS. Ur fellak a ten têasbev deg wacemma, ur fellasen a k êasben, deg wacemma. Ma terriv ten, ihi, a ppiliv seg imednas"
  6,53,"Akka ay Nhewwel kra s wiyav, iwakken a d inin: \"day d wigi i I$at Öebbi, garane$\"? Day ur Issin ara Öebbi, sennig akw, wid isnemmiren"
  6,54,"Ma usan k id wid iumnen s issekniyen nne£, ini: \"tifrat fellawen\"! Mass nnwen Iura, i iman iS, aêunu. Ihi, i win, segwen, ixedmen tucmip, ur iâammed, sin akin, isteôoaâ, u ixdem ayen ilhan, Neppa Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu"
  6,55,"Akka ay Nfeûûel issekniyen, iwakken a d iban ubrid ibe$wviyen"
  6,56,"Ini: \"nek, ippugdel iyi ad âabde$ wid u$uô la tepnujum, war Öebbi\". Ini: \"ur teddu$ d lemcihwat nnwen, mulac ad nnetlafe$, ur ppili$ seg wid ipwanhan"
  6,57,"Ini: \"nek, îîfe$ deg ubeggen n Mass iw. Teskaddbem t. Ur illi $uôi wayen u$uô têarem. Ih, aêuddu $eô Öebbi kan. Issawal tidep. Neppa Yif akw wid issenqaden"
  6,58,"Ini: \"lemmer illi $uôi wayen u$uô têarem, yili iûaô lameô, gari yidwen\". Öebbi Yif akw akken Issen imednas"
  6,59,"£uôeS tisura n tbavnit. Siwa Neppa itent Issnen. Iéôa i illan di lberr, di yill. Ur i$elli ifer siwa ma Iéôa t. Akken aâqqa di tillas n tmurt, tizzegzewt, ta$eôt, akw di tezmamt ipbegginen"
  6,60,"D Neppa i wen ippaddamen leôwaê deg iv. Iéôa ay txeddmem, deg wass. Sinna, Ippara kwen id degs, iwakken ad ivôu lajel ipwassnen. Sinna, $uôeS tu$alin nnwen, sinna, a kwen Ixebbeô $ef wayen txeddmem"
  6,61,"D Neppa ay d Aqehhaô sennig imdanen iS. Ippazen ed $uôwen imêaraben, alamma, ma tusa d tmeppant ar yiwen segwen, ad ddmen ôôuê is, imceggâen nne£. Nitni ur stehzayen"
  6,62,"Sinna, ad u$alen ar Öebbi, Bab nnsen n tidep. Aêuddu, day maççi d ayla S? Neppa Yif akw akken Ip$awal ar uqeîîi"
  6,63,"Ini: \"anwa ara kwen Isellken si tillas n lberr d yill, u$uô tnujem s uêiwet akked tugwdi\"? \"Ma Isellek a$ si tagi, war ccekk, a nili seg wid isnemmiren"
  6,64,"Ini: \"Öebbi Isellek ikwen segs, akw si yal lhemm, sinna, kunwi la tepcarakem"
  6,65,"Ini: \"Neppa, Izmer ad awen d Iazen aâaqeb sennig wen, ne$ seddaw ivaôen nnwen. Ne$ a kwen Issemfaôaq, kra segwen ad jeôôben leqheô n wiyav\". Wali amek id Nemmal issekniyen, amar ad meêûen"
  6,66,"Iskaddeb it ugdud ik, u neppa d tidep. Ini: \"ur awen lli$ d awkil"
  6,67,Yal asali s lweqt is. A ppu$alem a ppeéôem
  6,68,"Ma twalav wid ipnamaren $ef issekniyen nne£, eoo iten, alamma bedlen anamer. Ma iseppu k Cciîan, mi d temmektiv, ur p$imi d ugdud imednas"
  6,69,"Ur isefk ara i wid ipêezziben, a ten êasben deg wacemma. Maca d asmekti, amar ad êezzben"
  6,70,"Eoo wid irran ddin nnsen d urar, d aqesseô. T$uôô iten tmeddurt n ddunit. Mmekti d yis, ard a ipwaîîef umdan $ef wayen ikseb. Ur isâi, war Öebbi, bab ne$ amcafaâ. Yal le$ôama ur tepwaqbal segs. Widak d wid ipwaîfen $ef wayen kesben. I nitni tissit iô$an, aâaqeb aqeôêan, ilmend n wayen la jehlen"
  6,71,"Ini: \"day a nâaô, war Öebbi, ayen ur a$ neneffaâ, ur a$ neîîuôôu? U a nu$al a nwexxeô, deffir nnhaya n Öebbi, am win $ewwan ccwaîen di tmurt, u ippuêeyyeô\". Pnecciden t imeddukwal ar nnhaya: \"yya $uône$\"! Ini: \"d nnhaya n Öebbi, s tidep, ay d nnhaya. Nepwameô a nanez i Mass imavalen"
  6,72,"èéalet, êezzbet aS. £uôeS, Neppa, ara tepwafessrem"
  6,73,"D Neppa i Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan, s tidep. Ass ideg ara Yini: \"ili\"! Ad yili. Awal iS d tidep. IneS tagelda. Ass uûuvu n lbuq, Iéôa i iffren d wayen ivehôen. Neppa d Bab n ûûwab, i Iéôan"
  6,74,"Mi inna Ibôahim i baba s, Azaô: \"day a pperrev tiâancuôin d iôebbiten? Nek wala$ k, keçç akked ugdud ik, di ttelfan n ûûeê"
  6,75,"Akka, Nessken i Ibôahim, tagelda n tmurt akked igenwan, iwakken ad yili seg wid itebbten"
  6,76,"Mi t i$umm yiv, iwala itri, inna: \"wagi d Mass iw\". Mi ixsi, inna: \"ur êemle$ ara wid ixessin"
  6,77,"Mi iwala iuli d waggur n tziri, inna: \"wagi d Mass iw\". Mi i$ab, inna: \"ma ur iyi Inha ara Mass iw, ad ili$, war ccekk, seg ugdud im$eôôqen"
  6,78,"Mi iwala iîij ineqqeô ed, inna: \"wagi d Mass iw, wagi meqqweô kteô\". Mi i$li, inna: \"a yagdud iw! Nek rri$ akkin ayen tepcarakem"
  6,79,"Nek zzi$ udem iw ar Win Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan, male$ ar tidep. Ur lli$, nek, seg imcurak"
  6,80,"Ixuûem it ugdud is, inna: \"day ad iyi txaûmem $ef Öebbi? Ni$ Inha yi; ur ugade$ ayen i S tcurkem, siwa ma illa wayen i S ihwan i Mass iw. Tussna n Mass iw tezdi yal cci, day ur d tesmektayem ara"
  6,81,"Amek ara ugade$ ayen tepcarakem, ur tugadem mi kunwi tepcarakem, i Öebbi, ayen iwumi ur d Issers adabu fellawen? Anwa, ger sin ikabaran, i iklalen laman, maday tessnem"
  6,82,"Wid iumnen, ur sselsen ddens i liman nnsen, widak ad ilin di laman, u nitni pwanhan"
  6,83,"D wagi ay d awal nne£. Nefka yas t i Ibôahim, mgal agdud is. Nessalay tiseddaôin, win i£ £ ihwan. Ih, Mass ik d Bab n ûûwab, d Amusnaw"
  6,84,"Nefka yas Isêaq akked Yaâqub. I sin, Nenha ten. Nenha, zik, Nuê akw, ger tarwa s, Dawed, Sliman, Yub, Yusef, Musa, Haôun, - Akka ay Nepkafi iâaôviyen"
  6,85,"Zakarya, Yeêya, Âisa, Ilyas, - akw seg iâaôviyen"
  6,86,"Ismaâil, Lyasâa, Yunes, Luî, - akw Nesmenyaf iten $ef imavalen"
  6,87,"akw seg ibabaten nnsen, si tarwa nnsen, akked watmaten nnsen. Nefren iten, u Nebbwi ten d ubrid uwqim"
  6,88,"Tagi d nnhaya n Öebbi. Inehhu yis win i S ihwan, deg imdanen iS. Lemmer curken, war ccekk, ad asen imêu wayen xeddmen"
  6,89,"D wigi iwumi d Nebbwi Tazmamt, ûûwab, akked lambiyya. Ma jehlen widak yis, ihi, Nekwni Nwekkel ip i ugdud ur njehhel yis"
  6,90,"Wigi d wid Inha Öebbi. Ddu d nnhaya nnsen. Ini: \"ur awen suture$, fellas, taqdiât. Neppa d asmekti kan i imavalen"
  6,91,"Ur qudôen Öebbi azal n lqedô iS, mi qqaôen: \"ur d Issers Öebbi acemma ar umdan\". Ini: \"anwa id Issersen Tazmamt, id ibbwi Musa, d tafat u d nnhaya i medden? Tepparam p di lkwa$ev i tesskanem. Aîas ay teppeffrem. Tlemdem ayen ur tessinem, kunwi akked imezwura nnwen\". Ini: \"D Öebbi\". Sinna, anef asen ad uraren s nnmara nnsen"
  6,92,"Tagi d Tazmamt, Nessers ip id teôqa, a ptebbet ayen ip id izwaren, a ppendeô tayimmap n temdinin akked wayen i s d izzin. Wid iumnen s laxeôt, umnen yis. Nitni bedden i téilla nnsen"
  6,93,"Anwa idensen sennig win d igren tikerkas $ef Öebbi? Ne$ inna: \"ppuweêêa$ d\", ur as d ippuweêêa wacemma? U win innan: \"a d sserse$ am wayen id Issers Öebbi\"? Lemmer a pwaliv imednas, di maylellif n tmeppant, u lmalayek élent ed ifassen nnsent: \"ssuff$et ed tiôwiêin nnwen. Assa, a ppeppuqeîîim s uâaqeb isneêcamen, ilmend n wayen teqqaôem $ef Öebbi, ur d tidep. U tellam tessem$waôem iman nnwen, $ef issekniyen iS"
  6,94,"Ni$ tusam a£ d, d ifôiden, akken ikwen Nexleq abrid amezwaru. Teooam deffir wen, ayen i wen Nefka. Ur Nwala, $uôwen, imcafâen nnwen, wid i tâabdem, nitni, d icriken nnwen. Ni$ temfaôaqem, u ooan kwen wid la tâabdem"
  6,95,"Öebbi, s tidep, Ifeôôec aâqqa, i$es. Issuffu$ ed amuddir si lmegget. Issuffu$ ed lmegget seg umuddir. Akka ay d Öebbi. Acimi tugim"
  6,96,"Issenkar tafrara. Irra iv i ureyyeê, iîij d waggur i leêsab. D wagi ay d aseyyi n Uzmir, Amusnaw"
  6,97,"D Neppa i wen Irran itran, ad awen mlen abrid, di tillas n lberr akked yill. Ni$ Nemmal issekniyen i ugdud issnen"
  6,98,"D Neppa ikwen id Ixelqen si yiman afôid, sinna: amkan, tarusi. Ni$ Nemmal issekniyen i ugdud ifehhmen"
  6,99,"D Neppa id Isrusun aman seg igenni. Nessuffu$ ed yissen yal im$an. Nessuffu$ ed yissen tizzegzewt. Nessuffu$ ed yissen iâaqqayen mbabben, iguza n ppmeô id ipûubbun si tezdayin, leonanat n tfeôôant, uzemmur, n ôemman, ppemcabin ne$ ur ppemcabin. Walit ppemôa nnsen mi d teffe$ tebbwa. Ih, deg waya, war ccekk, issekniyen i ugdud iumnen"
  6,100,"Rran i Öebbi, leonun d icriken, u Ixelq iten. Snulfan aS d arrac, tullas, ur éôin. Gedha s yiS! Ay Aâlay sennig wayen d qqaôen"
  6,101,"Axellaq n tmurt akked igenwan, amek ara Isâu mmi S, ur Isâi tameddakwelt? U Ixleq yal cci, u Neppa, yal cci, Issen it"
  6,102,"D wagi ay d Öebbi, Mass nnwen, ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa. Ixleq yal cci, ihi âabdet eP. Neppa d Awkil n yal cci"
  6,103,"Ur T tepsami tmu$li. Neppa Ipsami tamu$li. Neppa d Laîif, i Izôan"
  6,104,"Ni$ iusa kwen id ara twalim, s$uô Mass nnwen. Win iwalan, i iman is; win idre$len, mgal is. Ur lli$ nek d amêareb nnwen"
  6,105,"Akka ay Nessefham issekniyen, iwakken ad inin: \"tlemdev\", iwakken a t Nbeggen i ugdud issnen"
  6,106,"Ddu d wayen ik ed ippuweêêan, s$uô Mass ik; ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa. Eoo imcurak"
  6,107,"Lemmer i S ihwi i Öebbi, ur curken. Ur k Nerra d amêareb nnsen, ur telliv d awkil nnsen"
  6,108,"Ur naâlet wid u$uô la pnujun, war Öebbi. Axaîeô ad naâlen Öebbi, s lbe$wv, war tamusni. Akka ay Ncebbeê igiten is i yal lois. Sinna, ar Mass nnsen, tu$alin nnsen; a ten Ixebbeô $ef wayen xeddmen"
  6,109,"Ggulen s Öebbi, tagalit meqqwôen, ar ma iusa ten id ussekni, ar ad amnen yis. Ini: \"issekniyen ar Öebbi kan\". Acu i kwen irran têussem ar, xas ma iusa ten id, ur ppamnen"
  6,110,"A Neppi ulawen nnsen, d yiéôi nnsen, akken ur uminen yis abrid amezwaru. A ten Neoo di lbe$wv nnsen, d ider$alen"
  6,111,"Xas Nekwni Nessers asen d lmalayek, u mmeslayen asen d lmeggtin, u Nefser asen d, yal cci, zdat sen, ur ppamnen, siwa ma ihwa yaS i Öebbi. Maca, aîas degsen ur ssinen"
  6,112,"Akka ay Nerra, i yal nnbi, acengu. Ccwaîen, seg imdanen akw si leonun, ppemweêêin garasen awal uziyn i u$uôôu. Lemmer i S ihwi, i Mass ik, ur p xeddmen. Ihi, eoo iten ar wayen d snulfuyen"
  6,113,"iwakken ad mmalen $uôes ulawen n wid ur numin s laxeôt, a t ôavin, ad gemren ayen zerâen"
  6,114,"Day b$i$ amêaddi, war Öebbi? D Neppa i wen d Issersen Tazmamt, s ussefhem. Wid iwumi Nefka Tazmamt, éôan, ar neppat, ters ed s$uô Mass ik, s tidep. Ur ppili seg wid ipcukkun"
  6,115,"Awal n Mass ik ibbwev, s tidep akked lmizan. Ur illi ubeddel deg wawal iS. Neppa Issel, d Amusnaw"
  6,116,"Ma tu$ev awal i tegwti n wid illan di tmurt, a k telfen seg ubrid n Öebbi. Teddun kan d wayen nwan. Nitni snulfuyen d kan"
  6,117,"Ih, Mass ik Issen sennig akw, anwi innetlafen seg ubrid iS. Neppa Issen sennig akw, anwi ipwanhan"
  6,118,"Eççet ayen i$ef d immekti isem n Öebbi, ma tumnem s issekniyen iS"
  6,119,"Acu ikwen iu$en, ur teppeppem ara seg wayen i$ef d immekti isem n Öebbi? Ni$ Issfehm awen ayen i wen Igdel, siwa ma ipwaêeppem fellawen. Ih, aîas ay tellifen, s zzhu nnsen, war tussna. Ni$ Mass ik Iugar akw akken Issen wid izegren tilas"
  6,120,"Ekkset abekkav uvhiô akked uffir. Ih, wid ibbwin abekkav, ad ppuqeîîin $ef wayen xeddmen"
  6,121,"Ur teppet ayen i$ef ur d immekti ara, isem n Öebbi. Ih, ayagi d ixmiô. Ih, ccwaîen pweêêin i imeddukwal nnsen, a kwen namren. Ma tu$em asen awal, kunwi, s tidep, tcurkem"
  6,122,"Ma win illan d lmegget, Nessider it id, Nga yas tafat, iteddu yis ger medden, day d amedya s, win illan di tillas, ur izmir ad iffe$ segsent. Akka, ippucebbeê i ijehliyen, wayen xeddmen"
  6,123,"Akka ay Nerra, ad ppandin di yal tamdint, ibe$wviyen is, uqsiêen mavi. Ppandin kan i iman nnsen, ur faqen"
  6,124,"Ma iusa ten id ussekni, ad inin: \"ur neppamen, alamma iusa ya$ d ayen id iusan ar imazanen n Öebbi\". Öebbi Yif akw akken Issen, anida ara Ifk tabôap iS. Ad iôxisen, ar Öebbi, wid ibe$wven. Fellasen aâaqeb uqsiê, ilmend n wayen ppandin"
  6,125,"Win Ib$a Öebbi a t Inhu, ad illi idmaren is ar wannuz. Win Ib$a a t Itlef, ad Irr idmaren is deyqen, têeyyôen, amzun ippaâôav ad iali s igenni. Akka i Ippara Öebbi axerwaâ i wid ur numin"
  6,126,Wagi d abrid uwqim n Mass ik. Ni$ Nessefham issekniyen i ugdud ismektayen
  6,127,"I nitni, axxam n tifrat ar Mass nnsen. Neppa d Bab nnsen, $ef wayen xeddmen"
  6,128,"Ass ideg ara ten Ifser meôôa: \"a yagraw n leonun, ni$ tcerrâem deg imdanen\"? A d inin imawlan nnsen, seg imdanen: \"a Mass nne$! Kra segne$ $elten si kra, Nebbwev ar lajel nne$, i $ Terriv\". Inna: \"d times ay d tanezdu$t nnwen, ad degs twekkôem, siwa ma ur aS ihwi i Öebbi\". Ih, Mass ik d Bab n ûûwab, d Amusnaw"
  6,129,"Akka ay Neppara kra imednas d iêbiben n kra, ilmend n wayen keppben"
  6,130,"A yagraw n leonun d yimdanen, day ur kwen id usan ara imazanen segwen? Mmalen awen issekniyen iW, nedôen kwen $ef temlilit n wass nnwen agi\". Nnan d: \"ncehhed $ef yiman nne$\". T$uôô iten tmeddurt n ddunit. Cehhden $ef yiman nnsen ar nitni, s tidep, llan d ijehliyen"
  6,131,"Akka, acku Mass ik ur Isquccu tamdint, s ddens, ma llan imezda$ is d i$wefliyen"
  6,132,"I yal yiwen, tiseddarin seg wayen ixdem. Ur I$effel Mass ik $ef wayen xeddmen"
  6,133,"Mass ik d Asâay, d Bab uêunu. Ma ihwa yaS a kwen Ikkes, a d Inûef, deffir wen, ayen i S ihwan, akken ikwen id Ixleq si tarwa n ugdud nniven"
  6,134,"Ih, ayen i wen ippuâahden, a d ias, war ccekk. Ur tezmirem, kunwi, a ppesfunngem"
  6,135,"Ini: \"a yagdud iw! Xedmet akken tewâam, nek ad xedme$. Deqqal a ppeéôem iwumi ara telhu taggara n Uxxam\". S tidep, ur rebêen imednas"
  6,136,"Gan aS i Öebbi amur, seg wayen id Ifka n l$ella, akked lmal. Nnan: \"wagi i Öebbi –- di tikta nnsen -, wagi i icriken nne$\". Ayen gan i icriken nnsen, ur ippawev ar Öebbi. Ayen gan i Öebbi, neppa, ad yawev ar icriken nnsen. I icmet wayen id pêuddun"
  6,137,"Akka ay cebbêen icriken nnsen, i waîas n yimcurak, timen$iwt n tarwa nnsen, iwakken a ten squccen, u ad irwi ddin nnsen, fellasen. Lemmer i S ihwi i Öebbi, ur p xeddmen. Eoo iten ar wayen d snulfuyen"
  6,138,"Nnan: \"lmal akked l$ella yagi ppugedlen, ur ten itepp, siwa win i $ ihwan\". S tikta nnsen. Lmal iwumi gedlen iârar nnsen, lmal iwumi ur d ppadren fellasen, isem n Öebbi. D asnulfu mgal iS. A ten Iqeîîi $ef wayen d snulfuyen"
  6,139,"Qqaôen: \"ayen illan deg iâabbav n lmal agi, i ddker nne$ kan, ipwagdel i tlawin nne$\". Ma ilul ed immut, ad mlilen $uôes. A ten Iqeîîi $ef wayen d qqaôen. Neppa, s tidep, d Bab n ûûwab, d Amusnaw"
  6,140,"Ni$ xesôen wid in$an arraw nnsen. D tiderwect, war tussna. Gedlen ayen i s iten I$at Öebbi, snulfan d mgal Öebbi. Ni$ nnetlafen, ur pwanhan"
  6,141,"D Neppa id Ixelqen leonanat s iâricen, ne$ war iâricen, tizdayin, zerriâa n yal ûûenf, i wuççi; azemmur akked rreman ippemcabin, ne$ ur neppemcabi. Eççet si ppemôa nnsen, ma fkan d, efket leêqq is, ass u$ellet nnsen. Ur ssugutet. Neppa, s tidep, ur Iêemmel ara wid ipêawalen"
  6,142,"Si lmal, aggway d wussu. Eççet seg wayen ikwen Iôéeq Öebbi. Ur teddut d iberdan n Cciîan. Neppa, s tidep, d acengu nnwen n ûûeê"
  6,143,"Ïamt tyugiwin, snat u$welmi, snat umâiz. Ini: \"d sin n ddker i Igdel, ne$ d snat n nnta, ne$ d ayen illan deg iâabbav n snat n nnta? Xebbôet iyi d, s tussna, ma tessawalem tidep"
  6,144,"Seg ile$wman, snat, seg ubeqôi, snat. Ini: \"d sin n ddker i Igdel, ne$ d snat n nnta, ne$ d ayen illan deg iâabbav n snat n nnta, ne$ tellam d inagan mi kwen id Iweûûa Öebbi $ef waya\"? Anwa idensen sennig win id igren tikerkas $ef Öebbi, iwakken ad itlef imdanen, ur issin. Ih, Öebbi ur Inehhu agdud imednas"
  6,145,"Ini: \"ur ufi$ ipwagdel a t içç yiwen, deg wayen iyi d ippuweêêan, siwa ma illa d loifa, ne$ d idim immaren, ne$ d aksum n yilef - wagi, war ccekk, d lewsex -, ne$ îêegga s d$wel i war Öebbi. Win i$ef ippuêeppem, ur ib$i, ur ib$wiv, Mass ik, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu"
  6,146,"I wudayen, Negdel ayen akw isâan acaren, seg ubeqôi akked u$welmi, Negdel asen tassemt nnsen, siwa tin n iârar nnsen, iâabbav, akked wayen ipwaxelven akked i$san. Akka ay ten Nepkafi, ilmend n îîeôô nnsen. Nekwni, war ccekk, d At Tidep"
  6,147,"Ma skaddben k, ini: \"Mass nnwen d Bab uêunu iwsâan, ur ipwexxiô ssexv iS, af ugdud ibe$wviyen"
  6,148,"Ad inin imcurak: \"lemmer i S ihwi i Öebbi, nekwni akked imezwura nne$, ur ncurek, ur negdel acemma\". Akka ay skaddben imezwura nnsen, armi jeôôben ssexv nne£. Ini: \"day tesâam tussna ar a$ d tesseknem? Teppeddum kan d nnwaya, kunwi tesnulfuyem d kan"
  6,149,"Ini: \"n Öebbi timenna tunûiêin. Lemmer i S ihwi, yili Inha kwen akw"
  6,150,"Ini: \"awit ed inagan nnwen, ara icehhden ar Öebbi Igdel ayagi\". Ma cehhden, ur cehhed yidsen. Ur teddu d lhawiyya n wid iskaddben issekniyen nne£, akked wid ur numin s laxeôt, u pparan tanudda i Mass nnsen"
  6,151,"Ini: \"yyaw, ad ini$. I wen Igdel Mass nnwen: ur aS tepcarakem acemma; elhut ar imawlan nnwen; ur neqqet tarwa nnwen, di tigullelt - d Nekwni ara kwen Iôeéqen yidsen -, ur ppaéet ar lâaô, d uvhiô ne$ d uffir; ur neqqet amdan, d ayen Igdel Öebbi, siwa ma s lêeqq\". Ar waya i kwen Iweûûa, amar a pfehmem"
  6,152,"Ur pqeôôibet s ayla ugujil, siwa s wayen ilhan, alamma immeêtel. Weznet, ktilet s lewqama. Ur Nepkellif amdan siwa ar wayen iwumi izmer. Ma thedôem d, weznet, xas ma $eô llzem nnwen. Qadôet lemâahda n Öebbi. Iweûûa kwen $ef waya, amar a d temmektim"
  6,153,"D wagi ay d abrid iW uwqim, ddut degs. Ur teddut d iberdan ara kwen isîixôen seg ubrid iS. Iweûûa kwen $ef waya, amar a pêezzbem"
  6,154,"Sinna, Nefka Tazmamt i Musa. Tewqem i wid imaânen, tfeûûel yal cci, d nnhaya u d aêunu. Amar ad amnen s timlilit n Mass nnsen"
  6,155,"Tagi d Tazmamt, Nessers ip id, teôqa. Ihi, ddut yides, êezzbet, amar fellawen aêunu"
  6,156,"Ur d teqqaôem ara: \"ters ed kan Tezmamt $eô sin leoyus, uqbel nne$, ur neéôi d acu sselmaden"
  6,157,"Ne$ a d tinim: \"lemmer id ters Tazmamt $uône$, yili nif iten akken nepwanha\". Ni$ iusa kwen id ubeggen, s$uô Mass nnwen, d nnhaya u d aêunu. Anwa idensen sennig win iskaddben issekniyen n Öebbi, u iooa iten? A Nqeîîi wid iooan issekniyen nne£, s yir aâaqeb, ilmend n wayen la ppaooan"
  6,158,"D acu pôaoun, siwa ma ten id asent lmalayek, ne$ a d Ias Mass ik, ne$ a d asen kra issekniyen n Mass ik? Ass ideg ara d asen kra issekniyen n Mass ik, ur infaâ umdan liman is, ma, iu$ lêal, ur iumin ara, ne$ ur iksib lxiô, di liman is. Ini: \"gganit, nekwni, ih, la nepgani"
  6,159,"Ih, wid ibvan ddin nnsen, u gan ikabaren, ur tepkkiv yidsen deg wacemma. Lameô nnsen ar Öebbi kan, sinna, a ten Ixebbeô $ef wayen xeddmen"
  6,160,"Win id iusan s yise$, ines mraw i t icban; win id iusan s tucmip, ad ippuqeîîi s tin kan i p icban; nitni ur pwadensen"
  6,161,"Ini: \"nek, Inha iyi Mass iw, ar ubrid uwqim, d ddin n ddwam, win n Ibôahim, i imalen ar tidep, ur nelli seg imcurak"
  6,162,"Ini: \"ih, taéallit iw, iseflan iw, tudert iw, tameppant iw, i Öebbi, Mass imavalen"
  6,163,"Ur aS illi ucarek. Pwamôe$ d s waya: nek d amduâ amenzu"
  6,164,"Ini: \"day b$i$ mass, war Öebbi? U Neppa d Mass n yal cci\". Ur ikesseb yal yiman, siwa mgal is. Ur ipbibbi win ibubben taâkkwemt n wayev. Sinna, ar Mass nnwen, tu$alin nnwen. Sinna, a kwen Ixebbeô $ef wayen tellam temgaradem"
  6,165,"D Neppa i kwen Irran d igensas di tmurt. Irra, kra segwen, tiseddaôin sennig wiyav, iwakken a kwen Ijeôôeb $ef wayen i wen Ifka. Ih, Mass ik Ip$awal deg uâaqeb. Neppa, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu"
  7,1,Almû
  7,2,"Tazmamt ters ed $uôek, ur teppili segs lhejna deg idmaren ik, iwakken a pnabiv yis; u d asmekti i lmumnin"
  7,3,"Ddut d wayen id irsen $uôwen, s$uô Mass nnwen. Ur teddut d imawlan, war Neppa. Drus id tesmektayem"
  7,4,"Acêal n temdinin ay Nessenger. Tusa ten id tiyta nne£, deg ives nnsen, ne$ deg uqeggel nnsen"
  7,5,"Ti$ôi nnsen, mi ten id tusa tiyta nne£, siwa mi d nnan: \"ih, nella d imednas"
  7,6,"War ccekk, a Nesteqsi wid u$uô id Nuzen, a Nesteqsi imazanen"
  7,7,"War ccekk, ad asen Neêku, s tmusni, ur Nelli N$ab"
  7,8,"Awzan, assen, d tidep. Wid iwumi ééayet lweznat nnsen, widak d wid irebêen"
  7,9,"Wid iwumi fessuset lweznat nnsen, widak d wid ixesôen iman nnsen, seg akken sednasen issekniyen nne£"
  7,10,"Ni$, s tidep, Nesrekd ikwen di tmurt, Nerra yawen, degs, tamâict nnwen. Drus ay tesnemmirem"
  7,11,"Ni$, s tidep, Nxelq ikwen, sinna, Nmesl ikwen, sinna, Nenna i lmalayek: \"knumt i Adem\"! Knant, siwa Iblis. Ur illi seg wid iknan"
  7,12,"Inna: \"acu k iîîfen ur tekniv ara, mi k d Umôe$\"? Inna d: \"Nek, ife$ t. Txelqev iyi si tmes, Txelqev t si talaxt"
  7,13,"Inna: \"ihi, ûûub segs! Ur ak ippunefk ara a ppesme$wôev iman ik, degs. Effe$, keçç seg wid ixuûen"
  7,14,"Inna: \"Eoo iyi, ar ass ideg ara d kkren"
  7,15,"Inna: \"keçç, ih, seg wid ara iqqimen"
  7,16,"Inna d: \"imi iyi Tâammdev a$ewwu, ad asen qqime$, war ccekk, deg ubrid iK uwqim"
  7,17,"Sinna, ad asen d tekke$ zdat, deffir, yeffus, zelmev. Ur Teppafev, $eô tugwti segsen, asnemmer"
  7,18,"Inna: \"effe$ segs, d ameêquô ippuvegôen! War ccekk, ad Acaôe$ Loahennama s wid, segsen, i k ivefôen, akked yiswen akw"
  7,19,"A Adem, ezde$ Loennet, keçç akked tmeîîut ik, eççet seg wayen i wen ihwan. Ur pqeôôibet ttejôa agi, mulac a ppilim seg imednas"
  7,20,"I$ewwa ten Cciîan, iwakken ad asen d iban âaryan nnsen i illan iffer. Inna: \"Ikkes awen, kan, Mass nnwen, ttejôa agi, iwakken ur teppilim d lmalayek, ne$ ur tepwekkiôem"
  7,21,"Iggul asen: \"nek, i kunwi, d unûiê"
  7,22,"Isdull iten s u$uôôu. Mi âaôven si ttejôa nni, walan iman nnsen aâran. Lhan d la pcuddun, $ef iman nnsen, afriwen n Loennet. Issawel asen d Mass nnsen: \"day ur awen Gdile$ ara ttejôa nni? Ad awen Ini$: war ccekk, Cciîan, i kunwi, d acengu n ûûeê"
  7,23,"Nnan: \"a Mass nne$! Nvuôô iman nne$. Ma ur a$ Tsemmêev, ur Têunev fella$, a nili seg imexsuôen"
  7,24,"Inna: \"erset! Kra d icenga n kra. A pzed$em di tmurt, a ppezhum, tallit kan"
  7,25,"Irna: \"degs a ppidirem, degs a ppemmtem, segs a d teff$em"
  7,26,"A tarwa n Adem! Ni$ Nessers awen ed aceîîiv ara kwen issôen, ôôêuê, akked uceîîiv uêezzeb. Wagi yif iten\". Ayagi seg issekniyen n Öebbi, amar a d mmektin"
  7,27,"A tarwa n Adem! £uôwat a kwen ihewwel Cciîan, akken id issuffe$ imezwura nnwen si Loennet! Ikkes asen iceîîiven nnsen, iwakken ad asen issken âaryan nnsen. Neppa, war ccekk, ipwali kwen - neppa akked ccetla s - seg wanda ur ten tepwalim. Ni$ Nerra ccwaîen d imawlan n wid ur numin"
  7,28,"Mi xedmen ayen n dir, ad inin: \"nufa d akka ar imezwura nne$, u Öebbi Iumeô a$ d $uôes. Ini: \"Öebbi, s tidep, ur Ippameô ar wayen n dir. Day a d tinim $ef Öebbi, ayen ur tessinem"
  7,29,"Ini: \"Iumeô ed Öebbi lmizan. Zzit $uôeS udmawen nnwen di yal lekni, nujet $uôeS. £uôeS, s ddin iûfan. Akken ikwen id Ixleq, a ppu$alem"
  7,30,"Arbaâ Inha it, arbaâ iura ttelfan fellas. Nitni, s tidep, rran ccwaîen d iêbiben, war Öebbi. U $ilen nitni, war ccekk, pwanhan"
  7,31,"A tarwa n Adem! Ccebêet i yal lekni, eççet, esswet, ur sîuqqutet. Neppa, s tidep, ur Iêemmel ara wid isîuqquten"
  7,32,"Ini: \"anwa i igedlen ccbaêa n Öebbi, id Issuffe$ i imdanen iS, akked ôôeéq ilhan\"? Ini: \"ayagi, di tmeddurt n ddunit, i wid iumnen. I nitni kan ass n tnekra\". Akka ay Nfeûûel issekniyen i ugdud issnen"
  7,33,"Ini: \"Mass iw Igdel kan ayen n dir, d uvhiô ne$ d uffir, abekkav, tem$weô war ssebba, a pcarkem i Öebbi ayen iwumi ur d irs udabu, a ppinim $ef Öebbi ayen ur tessinem"
  7,34,"Yal lois isâa lajel. Ma iusa d lajel nnsen, ur t swexxiôen s ssaâa, ur t id ééaéan"
  7,35,"A tarwa n Adem! Ma usan kwen id imazanen segwen, mmalen awen issekniyen iW, wid ipêezziben, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, ur ppagwaden, ur $weblen"
  7,36,"Wid iskaddben issekniyen nne£, u sme$wôen iman nnsen fellasen, widak d at tmes, nitni degs ad wekkôen"
  7,37,"Anwa idensen sennig win id igren tikerkas $ef Öebbi, ne$ iskaddben issekniyen iS? Widak, a ten iêaz umur i sen iuran di Tezmamt. Alamma, mi ten id usan imceggâen nne£, ad ddmen leôwaê nnsen, ad inin: \"anida ten wid u$uô tepnujum, war Öebbi\"? A d inin: \"ur ten nufi\". Ad cehhden, $ef yiman nnsen, ar nitni llan d ijehliyen"
  7,38,"Inna: \"kecmet di tmes ar leoyus n leonun akked yimdanen, i kwen id izwaren\"! Yal tikelt ara ikcem lois, ad ixzu gma s. Alamma, mi mlalen degs akw, ad yini uneggaru nnsen $ef umezwaru nnsen: \"a Mass nne$! Wigi telfen a$, Aâqeb iten s tmes, berdayen\". Inna: \"i yal yiwen berdayen, maca ur teéôim ara"
  7,39,"Inna umezwaru nnsen i uneggaru nnsen: \"ur kwen smenyafen i nekwni, ihi jeôôbet aâaqeb, ilmend n wayen tkeppbem"
  7,40,"Ih, wid iskaddben issekniyen nne£, u sme$wôen iman nnsen fellasen, ur asen tellin tibbura igenni, ur keçmen Loennet, skud ur iâadda ara ul$em di tiî n tsegnit. Akka ay Nepqeîîi ibe$wviyen"
  7,41,"I nitni ameîôeê di Loahennama, ad $ummen s tmes. Akka ay Nepqeîîi imednas"
  7,42,"Wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan - ur Nepkellif i umdan siwa ayen iwumi izmer - widak, d at Loennet, nitni, degs, ad wekkôen"
  7,43,"A Nekkes i d igwran n dd$el, deg idmaren nnsen. Isaffen ad ppazzalen ddawat sen. Ad inin: \"ccekôan i Öebbi i $ Inhan $eô waya. Ur nepwanhu, lemmer ur a$ Inha ara Öebbi. Ni$ usan d imazanen n Mass nne$, s tidep\". Ad pwanecden: \"appan Loennet, tweôtem p, ilmend n wayen txeddmem"
  7,44,"At Loennet ad siwlen i at tmes: \"ni$ nufa i $ Iâahed Mass nne$, s tidep. Ma tufam ayen i wen Iâahed Mass nnwen, s tidep\"? A inin: \"Ih\". Iberreê uberraê garasen: \"xezzu n Öebbi i imednas"
  7,45,"wid iîîeôôifen seg ubrid n Öebbi, ssaramen t d uâwij, u nekôen laxeôt"
  7,46,"Garasen ssteô. £ef iqacucen, irgazen, ssnen ten akw, ar ûûiffat nnsen. Ad siwlen i at Loennet: \"tifrat fellawen\"! Ur p keççmen, xas ssarmen"
  7,47,"Mi zzint wallen nnsen ar at tmes, ad inin: \"a Mass nne$! Ur a$ Ppara s agdud imednas"
  7,48,"Ad siwlen at iqacucen i irgazen, ssnen ten ar ûûiffat nnsen. Ad inin: \"acu i wen d issuli wayen tjemâam akked wayen tzuxxem"
  7,49,"Day wigi d wid i$ef teggulem, ar ur sen ippak Öebbi aêunu? \"Kecmet Loennet, ur teppagwadem, ur t$weblem"
  7,50,"At tmes ad siwlen i at Loennet: \"smiret ed fellane$ aman, ne$ seg wayen is ikwen I$at Öebbi\". Ad inin: \"Öebbi, s tidep, Igdel iten i ijehliyen"
  7,51,"wid irran ddin nnsen d zzhu, d urar, u t$uôô iten tmeddurt n ddunit\". Ihi, assa, a ten Neppu, akken ppun timlilit n wass nnsen agi, u nekôen issekniyen nne£"
  7,52,"Ni$ Nusa ten id s Tezmamt, Nfeûûel ip s tussna. D nnhaya, d aêunu i ugdud iumnen"
  7,53,"Day la pôaoun kan veôôu s? Ass n tisin n veôôu s, ad inin wid illan, iu$ lêal, ppun p: \"ni$ usan d imazanen n Mass nne$, s tidep. Day nesâa imcafâen ara $ icafâen, ne$ ad a$ rren, a nexdem ayen mgirrden wayen nxeddem\"? Ni$ sxeûôen iman nnsen. Itelf iten wayen d snulfuyen"
  7,54,"S tidep, Mass nnwen d Öebbi. Ixelq ed tamurt akked igenwan di sdis wussan, sinna, Iâannec $ef usgeld. Ip$ummu iv s wass, ip$awalen $uôes. Iîij, aggur, akked yitran unzen i lameô iS. Day maççi ineS lxelq akked lameô? D Asaâdi Öebbi, Mass imavalen"
  7,55,"Naâret Mass nnwen, s wannuz, di tbavnit. Neppa, s tidep, ur Iêemmel ara wid izegren tilas"
  7,56,"Ur ssefsadet di tmurt deffir useêôet is. Naâôet eP, s tugwdi d usirem. Aêunu n Öebbi, s tidep, ar tama n lâuûam"
  7,57,"D Neppa id Ippaznen avu, d abecceô s uêunu S. Alamma, ma ibbub ed asigna aéayan, Nenheô it ar tmurt immuten. Nesse$li d syis aman. Nessuffe$ ed yissen yal ppemôa. Akka ay d Nessuffu$ lmeggtin, amendeô ma d tesmektim"
  7,58,"Di tmurt lâali, teff$en d im$an is, ma Irad Öebbi. Di tin icemten, teff$en d kan d iweqweqen. Akka ay Nepbeggin issekniyen i ugdud isnemmiren"
  7,59,"Ni$ Nuzen ed Nuê i ugdud is. Inna: \"a yagdud iw! Âabdet Öebbi! Ur tesâim ôebbi war Neppa. Nek ugade$ fellawen aâaqeb, ass ameqwôaêan"
  7,60,"Nnan imvebbôen n ugdud is: \"$uône$, s tidep, aql ak di ttelfan n ûûeê"
  7,61,"Inna: \"a yagdud iw! Ur illi dgi ttelfan. Maca nek d amazan s$uô Mass imavalen"
  7,62,"Bbwi$ awen d tibratin n Mass iw, a kwen neûêe$. Ssne$, s$uô Öebbi, ayen ur tessinem"
  7,63,"Day twehmem mi kwen id iusa usmekti s$uô Mass nnwen, ibbwi t id urgaz segwen, iwakken a kwen inabi, iwakken a pêezzbem, amar fellawen aêunu"
  7,64,"Skaddben t. Nsellek it, akked wid illan yides, di lbabuô. Ne$meq wid iskaddben issekniyen nne£. Nitni, s tidep, d agdud ader$al"
  7,65,"Ar Âad, gmat sen Hud. Inna: \"a yagdud iw! Âabdet Öebbi! Ur tesâim ôebbi, war Neppa. Day ur tepêezziben ara"
  7,66,"Nnan imvebbôen, wid ijehlen seg ugdud is: \"s tidep, $uône$, deg k tisselbi; $uône$, ih, keçç seg wid iskiddiben"
  7,67,"Inna: \"a yagdud iw! Ur dgi tisselbi. Maca nek d amazan s$uô Mass imavalen"
  7,68,"Bbwi$ awen d tibratin n Mass iw. Nek, i kunwi, d aneûûaê muman"
  7,69,"Day twehmem mi kwen id iusa usmekti s$uô Mass nnwen, ibbwi t id urgaz segwen, iwakken a kwen inabi. Mmektit ed mi kwen Irra d igensas, deffir ugdud n Nuê. Isem$weô aîas lqedd nnwen. Mmektit ed lxiô n Öebbi, amar a prebêem"
  7,70,"Nnan: \"day a$ d tusiv, iwakken a naâbed Öebbi Yiwen, a neoo ayen llan âabden imezwura nne$? Awi ya$ d ayen is la $ tessagwadev, ma d tidep ay tessawalev"
  7,71,"Inna: \"ni$ iwwet ikwen id ddell akked zzâaf s$uô Mass nnwen. Day ad iyi namren $ef ismawen i tefkam, kunwi akked imezwura nnwen, i wid iwumi ur d Issers Öebbi kra udabu. Ihi, gganit, nek yidwen seg wid ara igganin"
  7,72,"Nsellek it, akked wid illan yides, s uêunu s$uône£. Nessenger wid iskaddben issekniyen nne£, ur nelli d lmumnin"
  7,73,"£uô Tamud, gmat sen Üaliê. Inna: \"a yagdud iw! Âabdet Öebbi! Ur tesâim ôebbi war Neppa. Ni$ iusa kwen id ubeggen s$uô Mass nnwen. Tal$wemt agi n Öebbi, d assekni i kunwi. Ooet ep a ppeçç di tmurt n Öebbi. Ur p îîuôôut, mulac a kwen iêaz uâaqeb aqeôêan"
  7,74,"Mmektit ed mi kwen Irra d igensas, deffir Âad. Isseqâad ikwen di tmurt, tepparram lebôuj di swaêel, teqqazem ixxamen deg durar. Ihi, mmektit ed lxiô n Öebbi, ur ssexsaôet tamurt, s usefsed"
  7,75,"Imvebbôen seg ugdud is, wid isme$awôen iman nnsen, nnan i wuôhifen, wid segsen iumnen: \"day teéôam ar ÛüÜaliê d amazan s$uô Mass is\"? Nnan: \"ih, numen s wayen is id ippuceggaâ"
  7,76,"Nnan imzuxiyen: \"nekwni, s tidep, nenkeô ayen is tumnem"
  7,77,"Ëerrfen avaô n tel$wemt, gelzen lameô n Mass nnsen. Nnan: \"a Üaliê, awi ya$ d ayen is la $ tessagwadev, ma d amazan ay telliv"
  7,78,"Tewwet iten zzenzla, gwran d, deg ixxamen nnsen, d loeppat"
  7,79,"Iwexxeô asen, u inna: \"a yagdud iw! Ni$ ssawve$ awen d tabôap n Mass iw, neûêe$ kwen, maca ur têemmlem ara win ineûêen"
  7,80,"I Luî, mi inna i ugdud is: \"day a txeddmem lâaô ur ixdim yiwen, uqbel nnwen, deg imavalen"
  7,81,"Ih, kunwi tpeddum ar irgazen, tcehwam ten, war tilawin. Kunwi, ih, d agdud izegren tilas"
  7,82,"Tiririt n ugdud is siwa nnan: \"ssuff$et pen si temdint nnwen, nitni d imdanen issaramen tezdeg"
  7,83,"Nsellek it, neppa akked twacult is, siwa tameîîut is, teqqim akked wid igwran"
  7,84,Nesse$li d fellasen ageffur…Wali amek tevôa d ibe$wviyen
  7,85,"£uô Madian, gmat sen Cuâayeb. Inna: \"a yagdud iw! Âabdet Öebbi! Ur tesâim ôebbi war Neppa. Ni$ iusa kwen id ubeggen s$uô Mass nnwen. Ktilet, weznet, s lewqama. Ur îîuôôut medden di cci nnsen, ur ssefsadet di tmurt, deffir useêôet is. I kunwi yif it wayagi, ma d lmumnin ay tellam"
  7,86,"Ur p$imit di yal abrid, tessagwadem u tessefôa$em seg ubrid n Öebbi, wid iumnen yiS. Teb$am t d uâwij. Mmektit ed mi tellam d takwemmict, Iketteô ikwen. Walit amek tevôa taggara ifessaden"
  7,87,"Ma illa iumen urbaâ segwen s wayen is id ppuceggâa$, arbaâ nniven ur iumin ara. Üebôet ard Iêudd Öebbi garane$. Neppa Yif akw imêaddan"
  7,88,"Nnan d imvebbôen imzuxiyen, n ugdud is,: \"a k nessuffe$ a Cuâayeb, keçç, akked wid iumnen yidek, si temdint nne$, ne$ a d tu$alev ar ddin nne$\". Inna: \"xas nugi"
  7,89,"Ihi, nger ed tikerkas $ef Öebbi, ma nu$al ar ddin nnwen, mbaâd ma Isellek a$ Öebbi, segs. Ur a$ ilaq ara a nu$al $uôes, siwa ma Irad Öebbi, Mass nne$. Mass nne$ Issemêalleq i yal cci s tmusni. Nepkel $ef Öebbi\". A Mass nne$! Fru p garane$ akked ugdud nne$, s tidep. Keçç Tifev akw wid iferrun"
  7,90,"Nnan imvebbôen, wid ijehlen, n ugdud is: \"ma teddam d Cuâayeb, war ccekk a pxesôem"
  7,91,"Tewwet iten zzenzla, gwran d, deg ixxamen nnsen, d loeppat"
  7,92,"Wid iskaddben Cuâayeb, u$alen amzun ur zdi$en. Wid iskaddben Cuâayeb, d nitni ay d imexûuôen"
  7,93,"Iwexxeô asen, u inna: \"a yagdud iw! Ni$ ssawve$ awen d tibôatin n Mass iw, neûêe$ kwen. Amek ara $weble$ $ef ugdud ijehliyen"
  7,94,"Ur Nuzen ara nnbi ar temdint, mebla ma Newwet imezda$ is s cedda, akked lemveôôa, amar ad êiwten"
  7,95,"Sinna, Nerra ise$ deg umkan n tucmip, armi wexxôen, nnan: \"ni$ jeôôben imezwura nne$ lemveôôa akked ttrika\". Newwet iten deqzalla, nitni ur bnin"
  7,96,"Lemmer kan uminen u êezzben imezda$ n temdinin, war ccekk, ad asen Nelli lbaôakat seg igenni akked tmurt. Maca, skaddben. Nessemêalleq asen, ilmend n wayen keppben"
  7,97,"Day $ilen imezda$ n temdinin, ur ten id teppawev tiyta nne£, deg yiv, nitni îîsen"
  7,98,"Ne$ day $ilen imezda$ n temdinin, ur ten id teppawev tiyta nne£, deg wazal, nitni ppuraren"
  7,99,"Day $ilen sellken i tandit n Öebbi? Siwa agdud i ixesôen, i i$ilen sellken i tandit n Öebbi"
  7,100,"Ne$ day ur d Iban ara, i wid ara iweôten tamurt, deffir imezda$ is, ar, ma ihwa ya£, a ten Newwet $ef ibekkaven nnsen, a Nesle$ ulawen nnsen, d$a nitni ur sellen"
  7,101,"D timdinin agi, i$ef ak Nêekku, si teqûivin nnsent. Ni$ usan $uôsent imazanen nnsent, s ubeggen. Ur llint d tid ara iamnen deg wayen skaddbent uqbel. Akka i Iselle$ Öebbi ulawen ijehliyen"
  7,102,"Ur Nufi nnesba ar tegwti nnsen. Nufa, tegwti nnsen, d iballa$en"
  7,103,"Sinna, deffir sen, Nuzen ed Musa, s issekniyen nne£, ar Ferâun akked imvebbôen is. Densen ten. Wali amek tevôa d ifessaden"
  7,104,"Inna Musa: \"a Ferâun! Nek d amazan s$uô Mass imavalen"
  7,105,"D ûûeê, ur qqaôe$, $ef Öebbi, siwa tidep. Ih, usi$ kwen id, s ubeggen n Mass nnwen. Ihi, azen yidi At Isôail"
  7,106,"Inna: \"ma tusiv d s ussekni, zzi t id, ma tessawalav tidep"
  7,107,"Iveggeô taâkwazt is, appan d azrem n ûûeê"
  7,108,"Issuffe$ ed afus is, iban ed d amellal i imnezhen"
  7,109,"Nnan d imvebbôen n ugdud n Ferâun: \"wagi, s tidep, d aseêêar amusnaw"
  7,110,"Ib$a a kwen issuffe$ si tmurt nnwen, d acu t lameô nnwen"
  7,111,"Nnan: \"anef as, neppa akked gma s. Azen iberraêen ar temdinin"
  7,112,ad ak d awin yal aseêêar amusnaw
  7,113,"Usan d iseêêaren n Ferâun, nnan: \"s tidep, ad a$ tkafiv, ma d nekwni ara i$elben"
  7,114,"Inna: \"ih, u, s tidep, a ppilim d iqôiben"
  7,115,"Nnan: \"a Musa! A pveggôev keçç, ne$ a nveggeô nekwni"
  7,116,"Inna: \"veggôet\"! Mi veggôen, sdehcen allen n l$aci, ssagwden ten. Bbwin d ssêur anect ilat"
  7,117,"Nweêêa i Musa: \"veggeô taâkwazt ik\"! Apan tesseblaâ ayen d ûenâan"
  7,118,"Tûaô tidep, inqev wayen xeddmen"
  7,119,"Akka ay pwa$elben. U$alen ar deffir, d unqisen"
  7,120,"£lin iseêêaren, knan"
  7,121,"Nnan: \"numen s Mass imavalen"
  7,122,Mass n Musa akked Haôun
  7,123,"Inna Ferâun: \"day tumnem yis, uqbel ma âammde$ awen? Ayagi, war ccekk, d tifxep. Tundim p di temdint, iwakken a ppessuff$em, segs, imezda$ is. Ihi, deqqal a ppeéôem"
  7,124,"War ccekk, ad awen gezme$ afus ssya, avaô ssya. Sinna, ih, a kwen semmôe$ akw $ef imudag"
  7,125,"Nnan: \"nekwni a nu$al ar Mass nne"
  7,126,"Terriv d ppaô segne$, imi kan numen s issekniyen n Mass nne$, mi $ d usan. A Mass nne$! Azen a$ d ûûbeô, Ddem leôwaê nne$ d imvuâen"
  7,127,"Imvebbôen n ugdud n Ferâun, nnan: \"day a ppeooev Musa akked ugdud is, ad ssefsaden di tmurt, a kwen ooen, keçç akked iôebbiten ik\"? Inna: \"a nene$ arrac nnsen, a nessider tilawin nnsen. Nekwni, sennig sen, d iqehhaôen"
  7,128,"Inna Musa i ugdud is: \"ppret afus n Öebbi, u ûebôet. Tamurt, war ccekk, n Öebbi. A p iwôet win i S ihwan, deg imdanen iS. Taggara i wid ipêezziben"
  7,129,"Nnan: \"njaf uqbel a $ d tasev, u deffir tisin ik\". Inna: \"amar Mass nnwen ad Ine$ acengu nnwen, a kwen Irr d igensas di tmurt, ad Iwali amek ara txedmem"
  7,130,"Newwet, d$a, lois n Ferâun s iseggwasen n llaé, akked nneqs n ppemôa, amar a d mmektin"
  7,131,"Ma iusa ten id ise$, ad inin: \"nne$ wagi\". Ma tusa ten id tucmip, a p sbibben i Musa akked wid illan yides. Ayen iveôôun yidsen, day maççi ar Öebbi kan? Maca, tegwti segsen ur ssinen"
  7,132,"Nnan: \" wicqa assekni ara d tawiv, ur a$ tepseêêirev yis. Nekwni, ur neppamen yisek"
  7,133,"Nuzen asen aêemmal, ajôad, tilkin, imqweôqwôen, idammen, d issekniyen ifeûlen. Sme$wôen iman nnsen. Llan d agdud ibe$wviyen"
  7,134,"Mi tevôa yidsen twa$it, qqaôen: \"a Musa! Nâaô Mass ik i nekwni, s wayen i k Iâahed. Ma tekksev a$ tawa$it, a namen yisek, a nazen yidek At Isôail"
  7,135,"Mi sen Nekkes tawa$it, ar lajel iten iggunin, atnan nitni xedâan"
  7,136,"Nerra d segsen ppaô, N$emq iten deg ill, imi skaddben issekniyen nne£, ur d celâen degsen"
  7,137,"Nessewôet i ugdud i illan qehôen t, igmav akked ituram n tmurt, i Neôqa. Itam wawal ûûam n Mass ik, $ef At Isôail, ilmend n wayen ûebôen. Nhudd ayen iûennaâ Ferâun akked ugdud is, u wayen bennun"
  7,138,"Nesâadda ill i At Isôail. Mmugren d agdud i iâabden tiâancuôin is. Nnan: \"a Musa! Err ane$ ôebbi am iôebbiten nnsen\". Inna: \"kunwi, s tidep, d agdud ur nessin"
  7,139,"Wigi, s tidep, ad inger wayen ideg llan, ad inqev wayen xeddmen"
  7,140,"Inna: \"day awen budde$ ôebbi, war Öebbi, u Neppa Ismenyaf ikwen $ef imavalen"
  7,141,"Mi kwen Nsellek si lois n Ferâun, sukken fellawen aâaqeb uqsiê mavi; neqqen arrac nnwen, ssidiren tilawin nnwen. Deg waya, ajeôôeb s$uô Mass nnwen ameqwôaêan"
  7,142,"Nemlal akked Musa kravet wavan, Nerna yasen mraw. Tebbwev tallit n Mass is, kuzet wavan. Inna Musa i gma s Haôun: \"enûef iyi ar ugdud iw, exdem ayen ilhan, ur teddu d ubrid ifessaden"
  7,143,"Mi d iusa Musa ar temlilit nne£, u Immeslay as Mass is, inna: \"a Mass iw! Ssenâat iyi d, a K wali$\". Inna d: \"ur iyI tepwaliv, d awez$i, maca muqel s adrar. Ma iqqim deg umekkan is, ad iyI twaliv\". Mi d Iusa Mass is s adrar, Irra t d saêel. I$li Musa, ixsef. Mi d iuki, inna: \"gedha s yiseK! Utube$ K, nek d amezwaru n lmumnin"
  7,144,"Inna: \"a Musa! Aql I Smenyafe$ k $ef imdanen, i tebôatin iW, i wawal iW. Ddem ayen i k d Fki$, ili seg wid isnemmiren"
  7,145,"Nura yas, di tlewêin, si yal cci, anabi akked ufeûûel n yal cci. Ddem itent s tezmert, ameô i ugdud ik a tent iîîef s lmaâna nnsent. Ad awen Ssekne$ tanezdu$t iballa$en"
  7,146,"Ad Veôôfe$, seg issekniyen iW, wid isme$wôen iman nnsen di tmurt, war ssebba. Mi walan yal assekni, ur ppamnen yis. Ma walan abrid uûwib, ur teddun degs. Ma walan abrid n le$wlav, a t awin. Ayagi, acku, s tidep, skaddben issekniyen nne£, ur d celâen degsen"
  7,147,"Wid iskaddben issekniyen nne£, akked temlilit n laxeôt, ur swin igiten nnsen. Day a ten kafin $ef wayen ur nelli d ayen xeddmen"
  7,148,"Agdud n Musa, deffir es, isbedd, s ôôêuê is, aâjmi bu loeppa isrugmuten. Day ur walan ara ar, s tidep, ur asen d ipmeslay, ur la ten inehhu s abrid? Âabden t, llan d imednas"
  7,149,"Mi ppuêeccmen, u walan ar, zi$ nnetlafen, nnan: \"ma ur Iêun ara fella$ Mass nne$, ma ur a$ Isemmeê ara, war ccekk, a nu$al seg imexsuôen"
  7,150,"Mi d iu$al Musa ar ugdud is, s wurrif akked lêemûa, inna: \"ay d ucmit wayen is iyi tneûfem, deffir iw! Teb$am a d i$iwwel lameô n Mass nnwen\"? Iveggeô tilewêin, iîîef gma s seg uqeôôu, ijebt it id $uôes. Inna d: \"a mmi s n yimma, s tidep, iêqeô iyi ugdud, qôib iyi n$an. Ur ssefôaê icenga yissi. Ur iyi pparra seg ugdud imednas"
  7,151,"Inna: \"a Mass iw! Semmeê ane$, nek akked gma, Ssekcem a$ ar uêunu K. Keçç, Tifev akw wid ipêunun"
  7,152,"Ih, wid iâabden aâajmi, a d i$li fellasen wurrif n Mass nnsen, ad ndellen di tmeddurt n ddunit. Akka ay Nepqeîîi wid id isnulfuyen"
  7,153,"Wid ixedmen tucmitin, sinna, steôoâen deffir sent, u umnen, Mass ik, s tidep, deffir sent, ar Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu"
  7,154,"Mi irs wurrif is, iddem ed Musa tilewêin. Di tira nnsent, nnhaya akked uêunu i wid ippagwaden Mass nnsen"
  7,155,"Ifren ed Musa ûatet irgazen seg ugdud is, ad mlilen yidne£. Mi ten tewwet zzenzla, inna: \"a Mass iw! Lemmer i K ihwi, yili, iu$ lêal, Ten$iv ten, u Tegliv yissi. Day ad a$ Temêuv, ilmend n wayen xedmen ije$lufen segne$? Wagi d ahewwel iK kan, Tettellifev syis win i K ihwan, Tnehhuv win i K ihwan. Keçç d Bab nne$, Semmeê a$, Ëun fella$, Keçç Tifev akw wid ipsemmiêen"
  7,156,"Aru ya$ ise$ di ddunit, di laxeôt; aql a$ nu$al ed $uôeK\". Inna d: \"aâaqeb iW, a t Sâaddi$ $ef win iyI ihwan. Aêunu W ijemmel yal cci. A t Aru$ i wid ipêezziben, ipzekkin, akked wid iumnen s issekniyen nne£"
  7,157,"wid iteddun d Umazan, Nnbi ur ne$ôi, i ufan iura $uôsen di Tuôa akked Linoil\". Iumeô asen d lqanun, Itekkes asen ayen n dir. Iêell asen lâali, igdel asen dduni. Ikkes asen aruz akked lqid nnsen. Ihi, wid iumnen yis, i t iâawnen, i t isellken, iddan d tafat id irsen yides, widak d imerbaê"
  7,158,"Ini: \"a yimdanen! Nek d Amazan n Öebbi $uôwen meôôa. Neppa, ineS tagelda n tmurt akked igenwan. Ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa. Issidir, Ineqq\". Ihi, amnet s Öebbi akked Umazan iS, Nnbi ur ne$ôi, i iumnen s Öebbi akked wawal iS. Ddut yides, amar a ppepwanhum"
  7,159,"Deg ugdud n Musa, arbaâ iteddu s tidep. U syis ay pêuddun"
  7,160,"Nessemfaôaq iten $ef mrawsin laâôac, n leoyus. Mi s issuter ugdud is tissit, Nweêêa i Musa: ewwet aéôu s tâakwaz ik. F$ent ed segs mrawsnat tliwa; akka, yal amdan iéôa anda ara issew. Nesbur iten s usigna, Nessers asen d lmenna akked ifeôôuoen: \"eççet seg wayen ilhan, is ikwen N$at\". Ur a£ dnisen, maca la ddennisen iman nnsen"
  7,161,"Mi pwanecden: \"zed$et di temdint agi, eççet segs, ayen i wen ihwan, init: \"laâfu\"! Âaddit di tebburt, s lekni. Ad awen Nsemmeê tuccva nnwen. A Nernu i lâuûam"
  7,162,"Wid idensen segsen, neûfen awalen s wid ur nelli d wid i sen nnan. Nuzen asen tiyta seg igenni, ilmend n wayen ddennisen"
  7,163,"Steqsi ten $ef temdint i illan $ef rrif n yill, mi ur d rzin di ssebt, mi ten id usan iselman nnsen, walan ten, ass n ssebt. Ass, war ssebt, ur ten id ppasen. Akka ay ten Njeôôeb, deg wayen ssexsaôen"
  7,164,"Mi d inna lois, segsen: \"iwumi la tepnabim agdud ara Isqucc Öebbi, ne$ ara Iâaqeb s leqseê\"? Nnan: \"d aste$feô ar Mass nnwen, amar ad êezzben"
  7,165,"Mi ppun ayen i$ef pwafekkôen, Nsellek wid itekksen ayen n dir, Nesâadda aâaqeb adiran $ef imednas, ilmend n wayen ssexsaôen"
  7,166,"Mi sme$wôen iman nnsen $ef wayen i sen ipwakksen, Nenna yasen: \"ilit d uddawen ucmiten"
  7,167,"Mi Ixebbeô Mass ik, ard asen d Iazen ara ten iâaqben, s ééuô, alamma d ass n tnekra. Mass ik, s tidep, Ip$awal ar uâaqeb. Neppa, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu"
  7,168,"Nessemfaôaq iten di tmurt, d leoyus, garasen wid imaânen, garasen wid ur nemâin. Njeôôeb iten s ise$iyen akked tucmitin, amar a d u$alen s abrid"
  7,169,"Neûfen ten, deffir sen, ineûûafen i iweôten Tazmamt. Ppaddamen lerbaê n ddunit, qqaôen: \"ad a$ semmêen\". Ma rnan usan ten id lerbaê, am widen, a ten ddmen. Day ur âahden ara s Tezmamt, ard tidep kan, ara inin $ef Öebbi? U lemden i illan degs. Ppif axxam aneggaru, i wid ipêezziben. Day ur tfehmem ara"
  7,170,"Wid iîîfen di Tezmamt, ipéallan, s tidep, ur Nveggiâ arraz n lâuûam"
  7,171,"Mi Nessuli adrar sennig sen, amzun d tili, $ilen, s tidep, ara d i$li fellasen. Ïîfet nezzeh ayen i wen Nefka, smektit ed ayen illan degs, amar a pêezzbem"
  7,172,"Mi d Iddem Mass ik, si tgeééal n tarwa n Adem, dderya nnsen, Inna yasen a d cehhden $ef yiman nnsen: \"day ur Lli$ ara d Mass nnwen\"? Nnan: \"ih, ncehhed\". Akka ur d teqqaôem ara, ass n tnekra: \"s tidep, ayagi d ayen ur neéôi"
  7,173,"Ne$ a d tinim: \"d imezwura nne$ kan i icurken, zik. Nekwni d tarwa deffir sen. Day a$ Ten$ev, ilmend n wayen xedmen wid iôejjnen"
  7,174,"Akka ay Nfeûûel issekniyen, amar a d u$alen s abrid"
  7,175,"Eêku yasen d tadyant n win iwumi Nefka issekniyen nne£. Irra ten akin. Idda yides Cciîan, iu$al seg wid i$eôqen"
  7,176,"Lemmer i £ ihwi, Nessuli t yissen. Maca, ib$a tamurt, idda d lhawiyya s. Ihi, amedya s am win n waydi, ma teddiv p fellas, ad ilehhet, ma teooiv t, ad ilehhet. D wagi ay d amedya n ugdud i iskaddben issekniyen nne£. Eêku d tadyant, amar a d mmektin"
  7,177,"Agdud iskaddben issekniyen nne£, d yir amedya. Pddennisen iman nnsen"
  7,178,"Win Inha Öebbi, ihi, idda d ubrid. Wid Itlef Öebbi, nitni d imexsuôen"
  7,179,"Ni$ Neswejd ed, i Loahennama, aîas n leonun akked yimdanen. Sâan ulawen, ur fehhmen yissen; sâan allen, ur pwalin yissent; sâan imeééu$en, ur sellen yissen. Nitni am lmal, ne$ nnetlafen kteô. Wigi d i$wefliyen"
  7,180,"I Öebbi, ismawen ûûam. Naâôet eP, yissen. Veôôfet seg wid issexsaôen ismawen iS. Ad ppuqeîîin $ef wayen xeddmen"
  7,181,"Deg wayen Nexleq, yiwen n lois ivfeô tidep. Ipêuddu syis"
  7,182,"Wid iskaddben issekniyen nne£, a ten Nawi, cwiî, cwiî, ar wanda ur éôin"
  7,183,"Ad asen Fke$ lmudda. Ih, ticeôkep iW d tunûiêt"
  7,184,"Day ur d tepmeyyizem ara? Ur illi umeddakwel nnwen d aôehbani. Neppa, d aneddaô kan ipbegginen"
  7,185,"Day ur walan ara tagelda n tmurt, igenwan, akked wayen Ixleq Öebbi n cci? Ni$, ahat, iqeôb ed lajel nnsen. Anwa awal, deffir wagi, ar amnen"
  7,186,"Win Itlef Öebbi, ur Isâi nnahi. A ten Ioo ad hemlen di tjehli nnsen"
  7,187,"A k steqsayen $ef yimir, melmi ara d yili. Ini: \"i t Iéôan siwa Mass iw. D Neppa kan a t id Isseknen, di lweqt is. Ad iaéay di tmurt akked igenwan. Ur kwen id ippawev siwa deqzalla\". A k steqsayen amzun tesâiv asali fellas. Ini: \"i t Issnen siwa ÔÖebbi\", maca tegwti n yimdanen ur ssinen"
  7,188,"Ini: \"ur ksibe$ i iman iw, aba$uô ne$ vveôô, kkes ed ayen Irad Öebbi. Lemmer ssine$ tabavnit, ad ôwu$ lxiô, ur iyi ipnal ixmiô. Nek d aneddaô kan, u d abcir, i ugdud iumnen"
  7,189,"D Neppa ikwen id Ixelqen si yiwen n yiman. Iddem ed segs tameîîut is, ad izde$ yides. Mi insa yides, tebbwi tadist tafessast; telêa yis. Mi d teûbeê ééayet, naâôen Öebbi: \"a Mass nne$! Ma Tefkiv a$ d aâeôvi, war ccekk, a nili seg wid isnemmiren"
  7,190,"Mi sen d Ifka aâeôdi, rran aS icriken s wayen i sen d Ifka. I aâlay Öebbi, sennig wayen pcaraken"
  7,191,"Day ad carken ayen ur nexliq acemma, u d nitni i ipwaxelqen"
  7,192,"Ur zmiren a ten âiwnen, ne$ ad âiwnen iman nnsen"
  7,193,"Ma tnecdem ten ar nnhaya, ur teddun yidwen. Iâuva fellawen ma tnecdem ten, ne$ ma tessusmem"
  7,194,"S tidep, wigi tnaâôem, war Öebbi, d imdanen am kunwi. Naâret pen, ma ad awen d rren, maday tessawalem tidep"
  7,195,"Day sâan ivaôen, ad lêun fellasen, ne$ sâan ifassen, ad ddmen yissen, ne$ sâan allen, ad walin yisent, ne$ sâan imeééu$en, ad slen yissen. Ini: \"naâret icriken nnwen, sinna, andit iyi. Ur iyi sganayet"
  7,196,"Ih, Bab iw d Öebbi id Issersen Tazmamt, i Iêemmlen lâuûam"
  7,197,"Wid tnaâôem, war Neppa, ur zmiren a kwen âawnen, ne$ ad âawnen iman nnsen"
  7,198,"Ma tnecdem ten ar nnhaya, ur sellen. A ten twaliv a k id pmuqulen, nitni ur pwalin"
  7,199,"Ddem ayen ilhan, ameô ar lewqama, veôôef i wid ur nessin"
  7,200,"Ma ilaâj ik Cciîan ar dduni, ppkel $ef Öebbi. Neppa, s tidep, Issel, d Amusnaw"
  7,201,"Ih, wid ipêezziben, ma innul iten urbaâ n ccwaîen, a d mmektin, d$a ad asen llint wallen"
  7,202,"Zgan $elîen atmaten nnsen, d$a nitni ur xevvun"
  7,203,"Ma ur asen d tebbwiv ara assekni, ad ak inin: \"acimi ur t id isnulfa ara\"? Ini: \"teddu$ kan d wayen iyi d ippuweêêan, s$uô Mass iw\". Wagi, s$uô Mass nnwen, d tafat, d nnhaya, d aêunu, i ugdud iumnen"
  7,204,"Ma qqaôen Leqwôan ssemêesset as, ssusmet, amar fellawen aêunu"
  7,205,"Mmekti d Mass ik, deg iman ik, s wannuz akked lxuf, s wawal irsen, taûebêit, tameddit. Ur ppili seg i$wefliyen"
  7,206,"Ih, wid illan ar Mass ik, ur sme$wôen ara iman nnsen, $ef uâbad iS. Sbuccuâen T, i Neppa kennun"
  8,1,"Steqsan k $ef rrbeê. Ini: \"rrbeê i Öebbi akked Umazan. Ihi, êezzbet i Öebbi, elhut garawen, a$et awal i Öebbi akked Umazan iS, ma d lmumnin ay tellam"
  8,2,"Lmumnin d wid kan iwumi ippergigi wul nnsen, ma Ipwabder ed Öebbi. Ma $ôan asen issekniyen iS, ad innerni liman nnsen. £ef Mass nnsen, ay ppeklen"
  8,3,"Wid ibedden i téallit, ipûeôôifen seg wayen is iten N$at"
  8,4,"Wigi d ûûeê, d lmumnin. I nitni, ar Mass nnsen, tiseddaôin, ssmaê, akked l$it uùkyis"
  8,5,"Akken ik id Issuffe$ Mass ik, seg uxxam ik, s tidep, wanag ur ib$i urbaâ si lmumnin"
  8,6,"La k pnamaren $ef tidep, deffir ubeggen is, amzun kan pwanehôen ar tmeppant, nitni pêekkiôen"
  8,7,"Mi wen Iâahed Öebbi, ara ppili nnwen, yiwet si snat n trebbuyaâ, tessarmem a ppili nnwen tin ur nepwaselleê. Öebbi Ib$a a d itebbet tidep s wawalen iS, ad ôéen wakali ijehliyen"
  8,8,"A ppili tidep, ad inqev lbaîel, xas ugin ibe$wviyen"
  8,9,"Mi tepprem afus s$uô Mass nnwen, Ijaweb awen d: \"Nek ad awen Fke$ agim lmalayek, mestebâant"
  8,10,"Irra t kan Öebbi d abecceô iwakken ad nnevmanen yis wulawen nnwen. Ur illi l$elb, siwa s$uô Öebbi. Öebbi, s tidep, d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab"
  8,11,"Mi kwen I$umm s yives, d îîmana s$uôeS; Isse$li d fellawen aman seg igenni; a kwen Izzizdeg yissen, ad Issebâad, fellawen, a$way n Cciîan, ad Isseohed ulawen nnwen, ad Itebbet, yissen, isurifen"
  8,12,"Mi Iweêêa Mass ik i lmalayek: \"Nek yidkwent; tebbtemt wid iumnen. Ad Skecme$ tugdi deg ulawen n wid ijehlen. Ewwtemt sennig tmegrav, ewwtemt ar ixfawen ivudan"
  8,13,"Ayagi, acku nitni, s tidep, xuûmen Öebbi akked Umazan iS. I win ixuûmen Öebbi akked Umazan iS, ihi, Öebbi Iwâaô deg uâaqeb"
  8,14,"Wagi i kunwi, jeôôbet ep! U i ijehliyen, aâaqeb n tmes"
  8,15,"A wid iumnen! Ma temmugrem d wid ijehlen la d éeddmen, ur sen reggwlet"
  8,16,"Win i sen irewlen, assen, siwa ma la issewjad i umennu$, ne$ ma ikcem s arbaâ, winna, a t immager wurrif n Öebbi; axxam is d Loahennama, a yir tu$alin"
  8,17,"Ur ten tennu$em, maca d Öebbi iten Innu$en. Ur teôoimev mi tôeomev, maca Öebbi Iôoem, iwakken ad Ijeôôeb lmumnin s ujeôôeb umâin s$uôeS. Öebbi, s tidep, Issel, d Amusnaw"
  8,18,"Akka, Ih, Öebbi Issadar ticeôkep ijehliyen"
  8,19,"Tessutrem l$elb, atan iusa kwen id. Ma tfukkem, ppif i kunwi. Ma tu$alem, a Nu$al. Ula iwumi tent, bippa, trebbuyaâ nnwen, xas îîuqtent. Ih, Öebbi Idda d lmumnin"
  8,20,"A wid iumnen! A$et awal i Öebbi akked Umazan iS. Ur T ppaooat, u kunwi tsellem"
  8,21,"Ur ppilit am wid innan: \"nesla\", nitni ur sellen"
  8,22,"£eô Öebbi, s tidep, ineggura imexlaq d iâeééugen, d igugam, ur nfehhem"
  8,23,"Lemmer Iéôi Öebbi degsen lxiô, yili Irra ten sellen. Ma Irra ten sellen, war ccekk, ad akwren avaô, u nitni aâûan"
  8,24,"A wid iumnen! Jawbet i Öebbi akked Umazan, ma Inced ikwen ar wayen ikwen issidiren. Cfut ar Öebbi Ippili ger umdan akked wul is. £uôeS, Neppa, s tidep, ara tepwafessrem"
  8,25,"Ëezzbet i uhewwel. Ur ipêaz ara kan imednas segwen, weêêedsen. Cfut ar Öebbi Iqseê deg uâaqeb"
  8,26,"Mmektit ed mi, kunwi, drus ay tellam, d uôhifen di tmurt, teppagwadem a kwen xevfen medden. Iûûeô ikwen, Isellek ikwen s l$elb iS, I$at ikwen s wayen ilhan, amender ma a ppesnemmrem"
  8,27,"A wid iumnen! Ur pxeyyinet Öebbi akked Umazan, ur pxeyyinet lamanat nnwen, kunwi teéôam"
  8,28,"Cfut ar, ayla nnwen akked tarwa nnwen, d ahewwel kan, u ar £uô Öebbi, ôôaîeb ameqwôaêan"
  8,29,"A wid iumnen! Ma têezzbem i Öebbi, ad awen Ifk afraz, ad awen Imêu tucmitin nnwen, ad awen Isemmeê. Öebbi d Bab n lfevl ameqwôaêan"
  8,30,"Ma ppandin ak, wid ijehlen, iwakken a k êebsen, ne$ a k n$en, ne$ a k ssuff$en; ppandin u Öebbi Ippandi. Öebbi Yif akw imendayen"
  8,31,"Ma $ôan asen issekniyen nne£, ad inin: \"ih, nesla. Ma ihwa ya$ a d nini am ayagi. Ayagi, s tidep, siwa d timucuha imezwura"
  8,32,"Mi nnan: \"a Öebbi, ma illa wagi d tidep s$uôeK, Sse$li d, fella$, id$a$en seg igenni, ne$ Awi a$ d aâaqeb aqeôêan"
  8,33,"Ur illi Öebbi d win ara ten Iâaqben, skud telliv garasen. Ur Illi Öebbi d win ara Ipâaqben ma nitni la suturen ssmaê"
  8,34,"Acimi ur ten Ipâaqab ara Öebbi, u nitni swexxiôen si Loamaâ n Lêaôam, ur llin d imawlan is. Imawlan is, d wid kan ipêezziben. Maca, tegwti segsen ur éôin"
  8,35,"Taéallit nnsen deg Uxxam, siwa aseffeô akked llir. Jeôôbet aâaqeb, $ef wayen tjehhlem"
  8,36,"Ih, wid ijehlen pûeôôifen ayla nnsen, iwakken ad veôôfen seg ubrid n Öebbi. A t ûeôôfen, ad asen iu$al d lexsaôa. Sinna, ad ppu$elben. Wid ijehlen ad pwafessren di Loahennama"
  8,37,"Iwakken ad Ifrez Öebbi dduni d lâali, ad Irr ixabiten, wa $ef wa, a ten Izdi akw, a ten Irr ar Loahennama. Widak d imexsuôen"
  8,38,"Ini i wid ijehlen: \"ma fukken, ad awen Isemmeê ayen iâaddan; ma u$alen, ihi, akken tevôa d imezwura"
  8,39,"Nna$et pen alamma tfukk lfetna, u iu$al ddin s lekmal is, i Öebbi. Ma êebsen, Öebbi, s tidep, Ipwali ay xeddmen"
  8,40,"Ma wexxôen, cfut ar Öebbi d Bab nnwen, Bab amxalef, Asellak amxalef"
  8,41,"Akken ib$u yili wayen id t$eltem n cci, cfut amur wis smus n Öebbi akked Umazan iS, akked llzem, igujilen, ime$ban, win d ibbwi ubrid; ma illa tumnem s Öebbi akked wayen id Nessers i umdan nne£, ass n ufraz, ass ideg mlalent snat n trebbuyaâ. Öebbi Izmer i yal cci"
  8,42,"Mi tellam di loiha taqôibt, u nitni agwemmav, imnayen seddawat wen, xas temyefkem ppaâud, tzeglem timlilit. Maca, iwakken ad Isâaddi Öebbi lameô ara iâaddin, ad immet win immuten, s ubeggen, ad yidir win idren, s ubeggen. Öebbi, s tidep, Issel, d Amusnaw"
  8,43,"Mi k ten id Issenâat Öebbi, d takwemmict, di targit ik ... Lemmer ik ten id Issenâat qwan, war ccekk, a pfeclem, a ppemnamarem $ef lameô. Maca, Öebbi Ijbeô ikwen. Ih, Neppa Issen i illan deg idmaren"
  8,44,"Mi wen ten Issenâat, mi ten temmugrem, twalam ten d takwemmict. Iééeméi kwen ar tmu$li nnsen, iwakken ad Isâaddi Öebbi lameô ara iâaddin. Ar Öebbi ppu$alen lumuô"
  8,45,"A wid iumnen! Ma temmugrem d arbaâ, tebbtet, mmektit ed aîas Öebbi, amar a prebêem"
  8,46,"A$et awal i Öebbi akked Umazan iS, ur ppemnamaret. Mulac a pfeclem, a pnegfem. Üebôet! S tidep, Öebbi ar iûebôiyen"
  8,47,"Ur ppilit am wid id iff$en s tem$weô, seg ixxamen nnsen, iwakken a ten id walin medden. Swexxiôen seg ubrid n Öebbi. Öebbi Izzi i wayen xeddmen"
  8,48,"Mi sen icebbeê Cciîan igiten nnsen, u inna: \"ur kwen i$elleb yiwen seg imdanen, ass agi. Nek d amalal nnwen\". Mi mwalant snat trebbuyaâ, iuker avaô, inna: \"nek xvi$ kwen, nek wala$ ayen ur twalam, nek ugade$ Öebbi. Öebbi Iqseê deg uâaqeb"
  8,49,"Mi nnan ixabiten akked imehzulen n wul: \"wigi, i$uôô iten ddin nnsen\". Win ippeklen $ef Öebbi, ihi, Öebbi d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab"
  8,50,"Lemmer a pwaliv mara ddment lmalayek leôwaê n wid ijehlen, ad kkatent udmawen nnsen, izugar nnsen. \"Jeôôbet aâaqeb n tmeô$iwt"
  8,51,"Ayagi ilmend n wayen d bbwin ifassen nnwen\", u Öebbi ur pdennis imdanen"
  8,52,"Am tikli n ugdud n Ferâun akked wid i ten id izwaren. Nekôen issekniyen n Öebbi. Issemêaleq asen Öebbi s ibekkaven nnsen. Ih, Öebbi d Uzmir, Iqseê deg uâaqeb"
  8,53,"Akka, acku Öebbi ur Ipbeddil l$it is I$at agdud, alamma bedlen i illan deg iman nnsen. Öebbi Issel, d Amusnaw"
  8,54,"Am tikli n ugdud n Ferâun akked wid i ten id izwaren. Skaddben issekniyen n Mass nnsen. Nen$a ten s ibekkaven nnsen, Ne$meq agdud n Ferâun; llan akw d imednas"
  8,55,"£uô Öebbi, imexlaq ucmiten mavi, d wid ijehlen, d$a ur uminen"
  8,56,"wid ukud tgiv lemâahda, sinna, di yal tikelt, neqven lemâahda nnsen, u nitni ur pêezziben"
  8,57,"Ma tugarev ten di îôad, sserwel yissen wid i ten id ivefôen, amar a d mmektin"
  8,58,"Ma tugadev lexdaâ seg ugdud, err iten akin, s tezdeg. Öebbi, s tidep, ur Iêemmel ara ixeddaâen"
  8,59,"Ur p$ilin menâan, wid ijehlen. Nitni, s tidep, ur zmiren"
  8,60,"Heggit asen d ayen iwumi tzemrem n lemêella akked yimnayen, a ppessagwdem yissen acengu n Öebbi, acengu nnwen, akked wiyav, war segsen, ur tessinem; Öebbi Issen iten. Ayen tseddqem n cci, deg ubrid n Öebbi, ad awen d iu$al. Kunwi ur tepwadensem"
  8,61,"Ma nudan talwit, nadi ep. Ppkel $ef Öebbi. Neppa, s tidep, Issel, d Amusnaw"
  8,62,"Ma b$an a k xedâan, ihi, âammed $ef Öebbi, Neppa i k Ifkan afus s tallalt iS, akked lmumnin"
  8,63,"Issemlal ulawen nnsen. Lemmer a pûeôfev i illan akw di tmurt, ur tessemliliv ulawen nnsen. Maca, Öebbi Issemlal iten. Neppa, s tidep, d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab"
  8,64,"A Nnbi! Âammed $ef Öebbi, keçç, akked wid iddan yidek si lmumnin"
  8,65,"A Nnbi! Eg lêir i lmumnin, ad nna$en. Ma llan segwen warem iûebôiyen, ad rnun snat twinas. Ma llan segwen twinas, ad rnun agim n wid ijehlen, acku, nitni d agdud ur nfehhem"
  8,66,"Tura, Issafes Öebbi fellawen. Iéôa tella garawen rrehma. Ihi, ma llan segwen twinas iûebôiyen, ad rnun snat twinas, ma llan segwen agim, ad rnun sin igima, ma Irad Öebbi. Öebbi ar iûebôiyen"
  8,67,"Ur issefk ara i Nnbi ad isâu imeêbas, alamma pwa$elben di tmurt. Teb$am tukci n ddunit. Öebbi Ib$a laxeôt. Öebbi d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab"
  8,68,"Lemmer maççi d ayen iuran s$uô Öebbi, izwar ed, yili a kwen iwwet uâaqeb abarar, ilmend n wayen tebbwim"
  8,69,"Eççet ayen ilhan, iêellen, seg wayen i t$elltem, êezzbet i Öebbi. Öebbi, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu"
  8,70,"A Nnbi! Ini i wid teîîfem seg imeêbas: \"ma Iufa Öebbi lxiô deg ulawen nnwen, ad awen Ifk ayen yifen ayen i wen ipwakksen, ad awen Isemmeê. Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu"
  8,71,"Ma b$an a k xedâan, ni$ iu$ lêal xedâen Öebbi. D$a, Ikkes asen ôôay. Öebbi Iéôa, d Bab n ûûwab"
  8,72,"Ih, wid iumnen, iunagen, ijuhden s wayla nnsen, akked yiman nnsen, deg ubrid n Öebbi, wid isnubgten u fkan afus, widak d imeddukwal bwaygarasen. Wid iumnen ur unagen, ur awen llin d imeddukwal, s wacemma, alamma unagen. Ma ppren afus nnwen di ddin, iwata yawen ad asen tefkem afus, siwa mgal agdud ukud tâaqdem. Öebbi Ipwali ayen txeddmem"
  8,73,"Wid ijehlen d imeddukwal bwaygarasen. Ma ur tgim ara akka, a ppili lfetna di tmurt, akked usefsed ameqwôan"
  8,74,"Wid iumnen, iunagen, ijuhden deg ubrid n Öebbi, wid isnubgten u fkan afus, widak, s tidep, d lmumnin. I nitni ssmaê akked l$it ukyis"
  8,75,"Wid iumnen syin $er da, u unagen, u juhden yidwen, widak segwen. Llzem ppemyilin kteô di Tezmamt n Öebbi. Öebbi, s tidep, Izôa yal cci"
  9,1,Öebbi akked Umazan iS kksen aêeppem i imcurak ukud tâaqqdem
  9,2,"Ddut di tmurt kué wagguren. Cfut ar kunwi ur tesfunnugem i Öebbi, u Öebbi ad Isdull ijehliyen"
  9,3,"Aberreê i medden, s$uô Öebbi akked Umazan iS, ass n êioo ameqwôaêan, ar Öebbi akked Umazan iS, kksen aêeppem i imcurak. \"Ma testeôoâam, ppif i kunwi, ma twexxôem, cfut ar kunwi ur tesfunnugem i Öebbi\". Becceô wid ijehlen s uâaqeb aqeôêan"
  9,4,"Kkes ed wid ukud tâaqqdem seg imcurak, sinna ur kwen bbwiven s wacemma, ur ullen yiwen mgal nnwen. Ïîfet di lemâahda nnsen ar lmudda s. Öebbi, s tidep, Iêemmel wid ipêezziben"
  9,5,"Mi âaddan wagguren iôqan, nna$et imcurak anda ten tufam. Ïîfet pen, êeôset pen, andit asen yal taxettalt. Ma steôoâan, ééulen, zekkan, ooet asen abrid. Öebbi, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu"
  9,6,"Ma issuter ak laânaya, yiwen seg imcurak, êareb fellas, ard issel i wawal n Öebbi, sinna, ssiwev it s amkan is n laman. Akka, acku nitni, s tidep, d agdud ur nessin"
  9,7,"Amek ara tili i imcurak, lemâahda s$uô Öebbi u s$uô Umazan iS, siwa wid tâahdem ar Loamaâ n Lêaôam. Skud sweqmen yidwen, sweqmet yidsen. Öebbi, s tidep, Iêemmel wid ipêezziben"
  9,8,"Amek, mi kwen $elben, ur kwen qudôen ilmend n yi$es, ne$ n lemâahda. Öuvan kwen s imawen nnsen; ulawen nnsen ugin. Tegwti segsen d iballa$en"
  9,9,"U$en s issekniyen n Öebbi ayen ôxisen. Ssefôa$en $ef ubrid iS. S tidep, ay dir wayen xeddmen nitni"
  9,10,"Ur qudôen lmumen ilmend n yi$es, ne$ n lemâahda. Wigi, ih, d wid izegren tilas"
  9,11,"Ma steôoâan, ééulen, zekkan, d atmaten nnwen di ddin. Nepfeûûil issekniyen i ugdud issnen"
  9,12,"Ma sêenten tagalit nnsen, deffir lemâahda nnsen, u wwten di ddin nnwen, nna$et iqweôôa n tijehli. Nitni, s tidep, ur ppaîafen di tgallit. Amar ad fukken"
  9,13,"Day ur tepna$em ara agdud i isêenten tagalit nnsen, u ib$an ad ssuff$en Amazan, u nitni heomen kwen d imezwura? Day ten tugadem? D Öebbi i iklalen a T tagwadem, ma d lmumnin ay tellam"
  9,14,"Nna$et pen, a ten Iâaqeb Öebbi s ufus nnwen, a ten Ixzu, a kwen Iserbeê fellasen, ad Icfu idmaren n ugdud n lmumnin"
  9,15,"Ad Ikkes urrif n wulawen nnsen. Öebbi Issuruf i win i S ihwan. Öebbi d Amusnaw, d Bab n ûûwab"
  9,16,"Day t$ilem a ppepwaterkem, wanag ur Iéôi Öebbi wid, degwen, ijuhden, ur neddi d imawlan, war Öebbi akked Umazan iS, akked lmumnin? Öebbi Iéôa ay txeddmem"
  9,17,"Ur issefk ara i imcurak ad kecmen leowamaâ n Öebbi, ad cehhden $ef tijehli nnsen. Widak neqven igiten nnsen, di tmes ad wekkôen"
  9,18,"Ara ikecmen kan leowamaâ n Öebbi, d wid iumnen s Öebbi akked wass aneggaru, iééulen, izekkan, ippagwaden siwa Öebbi. Ahat wigi ad ilin seg wid ipwanhan"
  9,19,"Day terram win i isswan iéaâlak, i ibedden i Loamaâ n Lêaôam, am win iumnen s Öebbi akked wass aneggaru u innu$ deg ubrid n Öebbi? Ur aâdilen ar Öebbi. Öebbi ur Inehhu agdud imednas"
  9,20,"Wid iumnen, iunagen, u nnu$en deg ubrid n Öebbi s wayla nnsen akked iman nnsen, aâlay umekkan nnsen, ar Öebbi. Wigi d wid ara irebêen"
  9,21,"Ibecceô iten Mass nnsen s uêunu s$uôeS, akked llza, akked leonanat, degsen ssaâd imezgi"
  9,22,"ad wekkôen degsen i lebda. Ih, ar Öebbi, arraz ameqwôaêan"
  9,23,"A wid iumnen! Ur pparat d imawlan, ibabaten nnwen akked watmaten nnwen, ma smenyafen tijehli i liman. Wid segwen i ten iran d imawlan, ad ilin, nitni, d imednas"
  9,24,"Ini: \"maday, sennig Öebbi akked Umazan iS, akked umennu$ deg ubrid iS, ay têemmlem ibabaten nnwen, tarwa nnwen, atmaten nnwen, tilawin nnwen, alag nnwen, ayla i tkesbem, ttjaôa i tugadem a ppe$li, tinezdu$in i kwen iâaoben, ihi, gganit ar d Ias Öebbi, s lameô iS. Öebbi ur Inehhu agdud iballa$en"
  9,25,"Ni$ Isrebê ikwen Öebbi deg waîas imukan, akked wass n Ëunain, mi kwen taâoeb îîaqa nnwen. Ur awen d tebbwi acemma. Tamurt iwsâan, tu$al awen tediyeq. D$a tezzim d, trewlem"
  9,26,"Sinna, Issers ed Öebbi talwit iS $ef Umazan iS, akked lmumnin, Issers ed iâsekôiwen ur tepwalim. Iâaqeb wid ijehlen. D wagi ay d aqeîîi ijehliyen"
  9,27,"Sinna, deffir waya, Öebbi Issuruf i win i S ihwan. Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu"
  9,28,"A wid iumnen! Imcurak maâfunit kan. Ur d pqeôôiben ar Loamaâ n Lêaôam, mara ifukk useggwas agi nnsen. Ma tugadem lqella, a kwen I$it Öebbi, s lfevl iS, ma ihwa yaS. Ih, Öebbi d Amusnaw, d Bab n ûûwab"
  9,29,"Nna$et wid ur numin ara s Öebbi, u s wass aneggaru, ur pgeddilen ayen Igdel Öebbi akked Umazan iS, ur xeddmen ddin n tidep, seg wid iwumi teppunefk Tezmamt, alamma xelûen tabzert s war amunnu, d imejjîuêen"
  9,30,"Nnan wudayen: \"Âuzayeô d mmi S n Öebbi\". Nnan imasiêiyen: \"lmasiê d mmi S n Öebbi\". Ayagi, nnan t id s imawen nnsen. Ppaâwaden d awal n wid ijehlen, n zik. A ten Ine$ Öebbi! Acêal îeôôifen"
  9,31,"Rran lquôôaê nnsen, ixelwiyen nnsen, lmasiê mmi s n Meryem, d imawlan war Öebbi. Pwamôen kan ad âabden Öebbi Yiwen; ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa. Gedha syiS, seg wayen pcaraken"
  9,32,"B$an s yimawen nnsen ad ssexsin tafat n Öebbi. I Ib$a Öebbi, ad Itim kan tafat iS, di nneqwma ijehliyen"
  9,33,"D Neppa id Iuznen Amazan iS, s nnhaya akked ddin n tidep, iwakken a t Issifer $ef ddin meôôa, xas ugin ijehliyen"
  9,34,"A wid iumnen! Aîas n lqweôôaê d ixelwiyen, s tidep, teppen d aêerfi ayla n medden. U îeôôifen seg ubrid n Öebbi. Wid ixeznen ddheb d lfeîîa, ur ten pseddiqen deg ubrid n Öebbi, becceô iten s uâaqeb aqeôêan"
  9,35,"Ass ideg ara ô$en di tmes n Loahennama, ad kwin, yissen, inyiren nnsen, ibeôdiyen nnsen, iârar nnsen. \"D ayagi ay txezznem i iman nnwen. Jeôôbet ayen txezznem"
  9,36,"Ih, ar Öebbi, amvan n wagguren: mrawsin; di Tezmamt n Öebbi, ass ideg Ixleq tamurt akked igenwan. Garasen, kué ôqan. D wagi ay d ddin n ddwam. Ur ddenniset iman nnwen degsen. Nna$et ijehliyen $ef ccfa, akken i kwen nnu$en $ef ccfa. Cfut, Öebbi Iteddu d wid ipêezziben"
  9,37,"Aswexxeô n waggur d timerniwt kan n tijehli. Nnetlafen yis wid ijehlen. Aseggwas a t êellen, aseggwas a t gedlen, iwakken ad wafqen amvan n wayen Igdel Öebbi. Ad êellen ayen Igdel Öebbi. Âaoben ten yir igiten nnsen. Öebbi ur Inehhu agdud ijehliyen"
  9,38,"A wid iumnen! Acu kwen iu$en? Ma nnan awen: \"hejjmet ar ubrid n Öebbi\", a ppebrum i iman nnwen. Day kwen taâoeb tmeddurt n ddunit, sennig tin n laxeôt? Zzhu n tmeddurt n ddunit d amejîiîuê kan, zdat win n laxeôt"
  9,39,"Ma ur tehjjimem ara, a kwen Iâaqeb s lqeôê, a d Iawi agdud nniven, deg umekkan nnwen. Ur T teîîuôum s wacemma. Öebbi Izmer i yal cci"
  9,40,"Ma ur t tsellkem, ihi, Isellek it Öebbi, mi t ssuff$en wid ijehlen. Wissin n sin, mi llan deg ifri, mi inna i umeddakwel is: \"kkes a$wbel, Öebbi, s tidep, yidne$\". Issers ed Öebbi talwit iS fellas, Iâawen it s iâsekriwen, ur ten twalam. Isse$li mavi awal n wid ijehlen. Awal n Öebbi, neppa, aâlay sennig akw. Öebbi d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab"
  9,41,"Hejjmet fessusit u ééayit, juhdet s wayla nnwen akked yiman nnwen, deg ubrid n Öebbi. Ppif wakka i kunwi, lemmer teéôim"
  9,42,"Lemmer d aba$uô isehlen, d inig wezzilen, yili vefôen k in. Maca, $wezzif fellasen umecwaô. Ad ggalen s Öebbi: \"lemmer nezmir, yili neffe$ yidwen\". Nn$an iman nnsen, Öebbi Iéôa ar nitni, war ccekk, d ikeddaben"
  9,43,"Ad ak Isemmeê Öebbi! Acimi i sen tserêev? Ard ak d iban anwi innan tidep, a ppissinev ikeddaben"
  9,44,"Ur ak d ssutren ara tsriê, wid iumnen s Öebbi akked wass aneggaru, mi juhden s wayla nnsen akked yiman nnsen. Öebbi Issen wid ipêezziben"
  9,45,"I k issutren tsriê, d wid ur numin s Öebbi akked wass aneggaru. Cukken wulawen nnsen, d$a, s ucukku nnsen, kukran"
  9,46,"Lemmer b$in tuff$a, yili heggan as d ayen ilaqen. Maca, Iugi Öebbi ad ppucegâan, Iurez iten. Nnan asen: \"qqimet d wid iqqimen"
  9,47,"Lemmer ffi$en yidwen, ar awen rnun siwa ccwal. War ccekk, ad kecmen garawen, b$an ahewwel nnwen. Kra segwen ssemêasen asen. Öebbi Issen imednas"
  9,48,"Ni$ b$an, si zik, ahewwel. Sxeôben ak lumuô, armi d tusa tidep. Ivehô ed lameô n Öebbi, nitni ur b$in"
  9,49,"Garasen win id innan: \"serreê iyi, ur iyi gar di lfetna\"! Day ur $lin ara di lfetna? Loahennama, s tidep, a ppezzi i ijehliyen"
  9,50,"Ma iusa k id yise$ ad $weblen. Ma tusa k id twa$it, ad inin: \"ni$, iu$ lêal, neqva lameô nne$\". Ad wexxôen, zzhan"
  9,51,"Ini: \"ur a$ ipêaz wacemma, siwa ayen i $ Iura Öebbi\". Neppa d Bab nne$. £ef Öebbi ara ppeklen lmumnin"
  9,52,"Ini: \"acu teggunim ad ivôu yidne$, siwa yiwen si sin ise$iyen? Nekwni negguni a kwen Iwwet Öebbi, s uâaqeb ara d iasen s$uôeS, ne$ seg ifassen nne$. Ihi gganit, nekwni a neggani yidwen"
  9,53,"Ini: \"seddqet, teb$am ne$ tugim, d ayen ur neppwaqbal segwen, d awez$i. Kunwi, s tidep, d agdud iballa$en"
  9,54,"Ay sen ikksen a tepwaqbal ssadaqa nnsen, imi kan jehlen, s tidep, ar Öebbi akked Umazan iS, u s laâgez kan ay d ppasen ar tpéallit, s usmiglez kan ay pseddiqen"
  9,55,"Ur k ippaâoab wayla nnsen, ne$ tarwa nnsen. Ib$a kan Öebbi a ten Iâaqeb yissen di tmeddurt n ddunit, ad iffe$ ôôuê nnsen, nitni d ijehliyen"
  9,56,"Ad ggalen s Öebbi, ar nitni, war ccekk, segwen. Ur nitni segwen, maca d agdud iugaden"
  9,57,"Lemmer ad afen ssôan, ne$ ifran, ne$ anda ara kecmen, ad ôuêen $uôes s tazla"
  9,58,"Garasen, wid ikkaten deg k, $ef ssadaqat. Ma ippunefk asen segsent, ad ôavin, ma ur asen ippunefk, ad neêwen"
  9,59,"Lemmer nitni, s tidep, ôuvan ayen i sen Ifka Öebbi akked Umazan iS, u nnan d: \"nesteqnaâ s Öebbi. Ad a$ d Ifk, si lfevl iS, Öebbi akked Umazan iS. Ih, d Öebbi i$ef neô$eb"
  9,60,"Ssadaqat siwa i ime$ban, iéawaliyen, i wid ice$wlen degsent, i usemlili n wulawen, i userreê imeêbas, i imeîîulba, i ubrid n Öebbi, i win d ifka ubrid. D aêeppem s$uô Öebbi. Öebbi d Amusnaw, d Bab n ûûwab"
  9,61,"Garasen, wid icettmen deg Umazan, qqaôen: \"neppa d aêessas\". Ini: \"d aêessas n lxiô i kunwi. Iumen s Öebbi, iumen lmumnin. D aêunu i wid iumnen segwen\". I wid icettmen deg Umazan n Öebbi, aâaqeb aqeôêan"
  9,62,"Ad awen ggalen s Öebbi, iwakken a kwen ôavin. Öebbi akked Umazan iS, Iklal kteô a T ôavin, lemmer llin d lmumnin"
  9,63,"Day ur éôin ara ar, win ixuûmen Öebbi akked Umazan iS, i neppa times n Loahennama, ad iwekkeô degs? D wagi ay d ddell abarar"
  9,64,"Ixabiten ugaden ad asen d ters tsuôep, ad asen tessken i illan deg ulawen nnsen. Ini: \"mmaâlket. Öebbi, s tidep, a d Issuffe$ ayen tugadem"
  9,65,"Ma testeqsav ten, a d inin, war ccekk: \"la nheddeô kan, nepqessiô\". Ini: \"day la tettihim di Öebbi akked issekniyen iS, akked Umazan iS"
  9,66,"Ur steôoiâat. Ni$ tu$alem ar tijehli, deffir liman nnwen\". Ma Nsemmeê i urbaâ segwen, a Naâqeb arbaâ, imi nitni llan d ibe$wviyen"
  9,67,"Ixabiten akked txabitin, wa ippameô i wa, ayen n dir, ppemyegdalen lewqama, pcuddun ifassen nnsen. Ppun Öebbi, Ippu ten. Ih, ixabiten d iballa$en"
  9,68,"Iwaââed Öebbi, i ixabiten, txabitin, akked ijehliyen, times n Loahennama, degs ad wekkôen. Beôka ten. Ixza ten Öebbi. Fellasen aâaqeb imezgi"
  9,69,"am imezwura nnwen. Llan ifen kwen tazmert, $elben kwen ayla, tarwa. Zhan deg umur nnsen, tezham deg umur nnwen, akken zhan imezwura nnwen deg umur nnsen. Teccvem akken ccven nitni. Widak, mêan igiten nnsen di ddunit, di laxeôt. Widak d imexsuôen"
  9,70,"Day ur ten id iusa ara usali imezwura nnsen? Agdud n Nuê, Âad, Tamud, agdud n Ibôahim, At Median, tid ippin. Usan ten id imazanen nnsen, s ubeggen. Ur ten Idennis Öebbi, maca llan dennisen iman nnsen"
  9,71,"Lmumnin, argaz tameîîut, d imeddukal wa n wa. Ppamôen lewqama, pgeddilen ayen n dir. Péallan, pzekkin, ppa$en awal i Öebbi akked Umazan iS. Wigi, ad Iêun Öebbi fellasen. Ih, Öebbi d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab"
  9,72,"Iwaââed Öebbi i lmumnin, argaz tameîîut, leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, ad wekkôen degsen; ixxamen igerzen di leonanat n Âaden, akked llza s$uô Öebbi - iten i$elben akw -. D wagi ay d rrbeê ameqwôaêan"
  9,73,"A Nnbi! Jahed ijehliyen akked ixabiten. Iqsiê $uôsen. Axxam nnsen d Loahennama, d taggara tucmip"
  9,74,"Ggulen s Öebbi ur d nnin, wanag nnan awal n tijehli. Jehlen deffir wannuz nnsen. Vemâen ayen iwumi ur wâan. Ur êzinen imi iten I$at, si lfevl iS, Öebbi akked Umazan iS. Ma steôoâen, yif it i nitni. Ma wexxôen, a ten Iâaqeb Öebbi s leqôeê, di ddunit, di laxeôt. Ur sâun, di tmurt, bab ne$ amâiwen"
  9,75,"Garasen, wid iâahden Öebbi: \"ma Ifka ya$ d, si lfevl iS, a nseddeq, a nili si lâuûam"
  9,76,"Mi sen Ifka si lfevl iS, a t bexwlen, ad wexxôen, ad namren"
  9,77,"Issegwra yasen d tanaâuôt deg ulawen nnsen, ar ass ideg ara mlilen yideS, imi xed$an Öebbi deg wayen i S âahden, imi llan skiddiben"
  9,78,"Day ur éôin ara Öebbi Issen sser nnsen akked wayen qqaôen u, ar Öebbi Issen tibavniyin"
  9,79,"Wid ipqeôôiven di lmumnin i ib$an ad seddqen, u deg wid i iufan siwa tazmert nnsen, d$a ttihin fellasen; ad Ittihi Öebbi fellasen. Fellasen aâaqeb aqeôêan"
  9,80,"Ssuter ad ppusemmêen, ne$ qqim. Ma tessutrev ûavet iberdan, ur sen Ipsemmiê Öebbi, d awez$i. Akka, imi nitni jehlen ar Öebbi akked Umazan iS. Öebbi ur Inehhu agdud iballa$en"
  9,81,"Wid igwran, feôêen mi llan deffir Umazan n Öebbi. Ugin ad nna$en s wayla nnsen akked teôwiêt nnsen, deg ubrid n Öebbi. Nnan: \"Ur pôuêut deg una$uô\". Ini: \"times n Loahennama teêma kteô, lemmer day fehhmen"
  9,82,"Anef ad vsen cwiî, ad run aîas, d aqeîîi n wayen keppben"
  9,83,"Ma Irra k id Öebbi ar urbaâ segsen, u ssutren ak d tsriê ad ff$en, ini: \"d awez$i, ur teppeff$em yidi, ur tepna$em acengu yidi. Akken, kunwi, iâoeb ikwen i$imi, abrid amenzu, ihi, qqimet akked ineggura"
  9,84,"Ur péalla $ef yiwen degsen, ma immut, d awez$i. Ur pbedda ar tenîelt is. Nitni, s tidep, jehlen ar Öebbi akked Umazan iS, mmuten nitni d iballa$en"
  9,85,"Ur k ippaâoab wayla nnsen, ne$ dderya nnsen. Öebbi Ib$a kan a ten Iâaqeb yissen di ddunit, ad asen teffe$ taôwiêt nitni d ijehliyen"
  9,86,"Ma ters ed tsuôep: \"amnet s Öebbi, jahdet akked Umazan iS\", imeôkantiyen nnsen a k ssutren tsriê, ad inin: \"anef ane$ ar wid iqqimen"
  9,87,"Öuvan ad ilin akked wid igwran. Ppusel$en wulawen nnsen, ur fehhmen"
  9,88,"Maca, amazan akked wid iumnen yides, jehden s wayla nnsen akked yiman nnsen. Widak, nnsen lxiô. Widak, d nitni ara irebêen"
  9,89,"Ihegga yasen d Öebbi leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, degsen ad wekkôen. D wagi ay d rrbeê ameqwôaêan"
  9,90,"Wid id iufan ssebba, seg waâôaben n ucluê, usan d, ad asen ifk tsriê. Wid iskaddben Öebbi akked Umazan iS, qqimen. Wid ijehlen, segsen, ad sâaddin aâaqeb aqeôêan"
  9,91,"Ur telli tuzzma $ef uôhifen, imuvan, wid ur nufi ara fken, ma neûêen ar Öebbi akked Umazan iS. Ur telli tuzzma $ef iâaôviyen. Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu"
  9,92,"Am akken, i wid ik id iusan a ten tneqqlev, tenniv: \"ur awen ufi$ ara kwen ineqqlen\". U$alen, allen feggvent seg imeîîawen, $weblen imi ur ufin ara sedqen"
  9,93,"Tuzzma kan $ef wid ik issuturen tsriê, nitni d imeôkantiyen. Öuvan ad ilin akked ineggura. Isle$ Öebbi ulawen nnsen, d$a ur ssinen"
  9,94,"Ad awen ssutren ssmaê, ma tu$alem d $uôsen. Ini: \"ur ssuturet ssmaê, ur kwen numin d awez$i. Ni$ Imla ya$ Öebbi asali nnwen. Ad Iéeô Öebbi akked Umazan iS, igiten nnwen. Sinna, a ppu$alem ar Umusnaw n wayen iffren akked wayen ur neffir, ad awen Imel ayen txeddmem"
  9,95,"Ad awen gren Öebbi, mi d tu$alem $uôsen, iwakken ad asen tanfem. Wexxeôt asen; nitni, s tidep, d laâôuô; axxam nnsen d Loahennama, d aqeîîi n wayen keppben"
  9,96,"Ad awen ggalen iwakken a ten tôavim. Ma tôuvam ten, ihi, Öebbi ur Ipôavi agdud iballa$en"
  9,97,"Aâôaben n ucluê zaden di tijehli akked nnxayel, zeggwiren ar uzgar n tilas id Issers Öebbi i Umazan iS. Öebbi d Amusnaw, d Bab n ûûwab"
  9,98,"Ger waâôaben n ucluê, wid iêesben ayen seddqen d tabzert. Ggunin a ppekêes fellawen teswiât. Fellasen abeddel adiran n teswiât! Öebbi Issel, Issen"
  9,99,"Ger waâôaben n ucluê, wid iumnen s Öebbi d wass aneggaru, êesben ayen seddqen a ten iééié ar Öebbi akked téilla Umazan. Day maççi, s tidep, d ayen ara ten iééiéen? A ten Issekcem Öebbi deg uêunu S. Öebbi, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu"
  9,100,"Imenza i izwaren, seg iminigen, imâiwnen, akked wid i ten iâanden ar lewqama, Iôuva ten Öebbi, ôuvan T. Ihegga yasen d leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, ad wekkôen degsen, i lebda. D wagi ay d rrbeê ameqwôaêan"
  9,101,"Ger waâôaben n ucluê, i wen d izzin, llan at sin wudmawen, akw ger imezda$ n Lmadina. Zgan di nnxayel. Ur ten tessinev. Nekwni, Nessen iten. A ten Nâaqeb berdayen, sinna, ad ppunefken i uâaqeb abarar"
  9,102,"Wiyad qaôôen s ibekkaven nnsen, ssemlalen igi ilhan d win nniven icemten. Izmer Öebbi ad asen Issuref. S tidep, Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu"
  9,103,"Eddem ed ssadaqa seg wayla nnsen, a ten tezzizdeg, a ten tûeffi. èÈéal ilmend nnsen. Ih, tiéilla k d talwit nnsen. Öebbi Issel, d Amusnaw"
  9,104,"Day ur éôin ara Öebbi, Neppa, Iqebbel asteôoaâ s$uô ixdimen iS? Ippaîaf ssadaqat. Ih, Öebbi Issuruf, Ipêunu"
  9,105,"Ini: \"xedmet! Ad Iwali igiten nnwen, Öebbi, Umazan iS, akked lmumnin. Tu$alin nnwen ar Umusnaw n wayen iffren akked wayen ur neffir, ad awen Imel ayen txeddmem"
  9,106,"Wiyav pganin lameô n Öebbi, a ten Iâaqeb, ne$ ad asen Issuref. Öebbi d Amusnaw, d Bab n ûûwab"
  9,107,"Wid irran loamaâ i lemveôôa akked tijehli, i lefôaq ger lmumnin; d taxettalt i wid, iu$ lêal, llan pna$en Öebbi akked Umazan iS, ad ggalen, war ccekk: \"ay neb$a siwa lewqama\". Ad Icehhed Öebbi ar nitni, s tidep, d ikeddaben"
  9,108,"Ur ppili, degs, d awez$i. Iklal kteô, tilin ik, loamaâ ibnan $ef uêezzeb, seg wass amenzu. Degs irgazen i iêemmlen ad izdigen. Öebbi Iêemmel izedganen"
  9,109,"Day win issersen lebni s $ef uêezzeb i Öebbi akked llza, ur yif ara win issersen lebni s $ef rrif n ucôuf ara iseggxen? Iseggex yis ar tmes n Loahennama. Öebbi ur Inehhu agdud imednas"
  9,110,"Izga lebni, bnan, ippara ccekk deg ulawen nnsen, alamma gezmen wulawen nnsen. Öebbi d Amusnaw, d Bab n ûûwab"
  9,111,"Ih, Öebbi Iu$ ar lmumnin, iman nnsen akked wayla nnsen, imi Loennet i nitni. Pna$en deg ubrid n Öebbi. Nn$an, pwan$an. D lemâahda fellas, s tidep, di Tuôa, di Linoil akked Leqwôan. Anwa yifen Öebbi di tuîîfa n lemâahda s? Feôêet, ihi, di ssuq tsewwqem. Wagi d rrbeê ameqwôaêan"
  9,112,"Wid isteôoâen, wid iâabden, wid ipcekkiôen, ixelwiyen, wid iîîinizen, wid ikennun, wid ippamôen lewqama, wid ipgeddilen ayen n dir, wid ipêaraben $ef tlisa n Öebbi ... Becceô lmumnin"
  9,113,"Ur issefk ara i Nnbi akked wid iumnen, ad ssutren ad pwasemmêen imcurak, xas ppilin asen, ma iban asen d ar, nitni, war ccekk, d at tmes"
  9,114,"Ibôahim ur issuter ara ad ipwasemmeê baba s, siwa ilmend n lemâahda i s ifka. Mi s d iban ar neppa d acengu n Öebbi, ifra p yides. Ibôahim, war ccekk, ippanez, iêellem"
  9,115,"Ur p Ixeddem Öebbi, ad Itlef agdud mbaâd ma Inha ten, alamma i sen Ibeggen acu ara êezzben. Öebbi, s tidep, Issen yal cci"
  9,116,"Ih, Öebbi, IneS tagelda n tmurt akked igenwan, Issidir, Ineqq. Ur awen illi, war Öebbi, bab ne$ amâiwen"
  9,117,"Ni$ Issuref Öebbi i Nnbi akked iminigen, akked imâiwnen i iddan yides, di lweqt uwâiô, mbaâd ma qôib nneqlaben wulawen n urbaâ segsen. Sinna, Issuref asen. Ih, Neppa, i nitni, dUmâin, d'Aênin"
  9,118,"U i krav id igwran, armi, tamurt iwsâan, tediyyeq fellasen. Vaqen deg iman nnsen. Ufan ur illi ssôan si Öebbi, siwa Neppa. Sinna, Issuref asen, akken ad steôoâen. Öebbi, s tidep, Issuruf, Ipêunu"
  9,119,"A wid iumnen! Ëezzbet i Öebbi, ilit seg imawlan n tidep"
  9,120,"Ur issefk ara i imezda$ n Lmadina, d wayen i sen d izzin n waâôaben n ucluê, ad gwrin deffir Umazan n Öebbi, ne$ ad smenyafen iman nnsen i iman is. Ayagi, acku ur ten ipêaz fad, ne$ âaggu, ne$ llaé, deg ubrid n Öebbi. Ur keçmen akal ara isserfun ijehliyen, ur ppaîîafen acemma s$uô ucengu, siwa ma dayen i sen iuran d igi n wayen ilhan. Öebbi, s tidep, ur Isôuêu arraz iâaôviyen"
  9,121,"Ur pûeôôifen cwiî ne$ aîas, ur zeggren asif, siwa ma iura yasen, iwakken a ten Ikafi Öebbi $ef wayen ilhan deg wayen xeddmen"
  9,122,"Ur Issefk ara i lmumnin ad ff$en akw. Awufan ad iffe$ ugraw si yal arbaâ, ad $bun di ddin, ad nabin agdud nnsen, mara u$alen $uôsen. Amar ad steêdren"
  9,123,"A wid iumnen! Nna$et ijehliyen i kwen iqeôben. Ad afen, $uôwen, teqseê. Cfut, Öebbi Ippili d wid ipêezziben"
  9,124,"Mi d ters tsuôep, llan garasen wid iqqaôen: \"anwa degwen, iwumi terna tagi, di liman\"? Ma d wid iumnen, terna yasen liman, u nitni feôêen"
  9,125,"Ma d wid iwumi blan wulawen, terna ammus i wammus nnsen. Mmuten u nitni d ijehliyen"
  9,126,"Day ur walan ara, ar nitni la d sskaren lfetna, yal aseggwas, yiwen ubrid ne$ berdayen? Sinna, ur steôoiâen, ur d smektayen"
  9,127,"Mi d ters tsuôep, ad mesmuqalen: \"day illa yiwen ikwen id Ipwalin\"? Sinna, ad wexxôen. Isswexxeô Öebbi ulawen nnsen, imi nitni d agdud ur nfehhem"
  9,128,"Ni$ iusa kwen id Umazan seg iman nnwen. èéay fellas laâtab nnwen. Ipêarab fellawen, d umâin, d aênin i lmumnin"
  9,129,"Ma wexxôen, ini: \"Iqadd iyi Öebbi. Ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa. FellaS ppekle$. Neppa d Mass n usgeld ameqwôaêan"